Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The SCLC has direct Communist ties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Even great men can be corrupted,  can't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Communism is not a political party.  It is a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It corrupts the soul,  turning even the gentlest of men...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...into vicious, evil tyrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:46.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What we are seeing is a pervasive  contempt for law and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Crime rates are soaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's widespread,  open defiance of our authority...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and, mark my words,  if this goes unchecked...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:58.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...it will once again plunge our nation  into the depths of anarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:01.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It all starts out peacefully,  doesn't it, Mr. lrwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to live with the fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:06.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you could've helped prevent  the bombings and the violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more interested in what this says  about your FBl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:11.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have worked too long and hard  to just sit back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:15.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and watch the bad guys capture  the spotlight again, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:17.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The funny thing about notoriety...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:21.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...especially the kind that needs adoration,  fame for fame's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...if unchecked,  it inevitably leads to villainy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you look at what this  squabble is really about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...before you destroy the reputation  of the thing we both know you love most.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:48.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, the writer's here from Crime Records...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:50.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the PR Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Set him up with a typewriter  in my outer office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, it's time this generation  learn my side of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right away.  - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:03.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In 1919, Agent Smith...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:05.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...my first boss here  at the Department of Justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...was Attorney General  A. Mitchell Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Quaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:15.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't believe in war, but he understood  the necessity of strength and resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe what you will from historians...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...most write from a present perspective,  forgetting context.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitchell Palmer was a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you all right?  - Unh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you all right?  - Yes. I think. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:22.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's all right, it's all right.  - No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see,  Palmer fought the radicals, just as I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And just as I have, he was targeted.  He wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:12.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Across the country that night,  eight bombs exploded, all at 11 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Two United States senators...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...four cabinet members,  a Supreme Court justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...John D. Rockefeller, J.P. Morgan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...all of them targeted  by Bolshevik Communists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it shook the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was clear to me  the radical's bomb went off too soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...leaving only his blood in the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:40.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But the inspectors used buckets to  clean up the mess instead of collecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They discarded his gun  instead of preserving its prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But you see,  this wasn't clumsy police work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In those times, it was normal procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be the end of days  for this country, Dwight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,it was 1919, before anyone  respected criminal science...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...before federal powers, before the FBl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:10.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that night my eyes were opened.  That very night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a neighbor, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He works in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:21.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- "There will have to be murder.  - We will kill because it is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We will destroy to rid the world  of your tyrannical institutions."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You were at Attorney General  Palmer's home that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's leave that  to the reader's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, it's important we give  our protagonist a bit of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I could allude to a young man  who matches your description.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The best of both worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you get your law degree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,George Washington. I grew up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a mom to take care of,  so I stayed close.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I received an English degree there also.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I don't need to tell you that  what determines a man's legacy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...is often what isn't seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's critical at this moment is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:12.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that we re-clarify the difference  between villain and hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think that compares  with today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, sir. I'd like to hear more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I could come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. But the pages stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Never a good idea to talk too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Palmer has asked that you attend  the emergency meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gladwell, please remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too early this time.  It's as rude as being tardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And who is this lovely addition  to the secretarial pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Helen, introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you, Mr. Hoover.  I'm Helen Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.  Welcome to the Department of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can notify Mr. Palmer  that I will attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:33.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- He's always a charmer.  - I wouldn't take anything very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeremy, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need, uh... Uh, help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Marcia held court this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:20.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I should buy a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She says your father will die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:29.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And when he does, you will rise to be  the most powerful man in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother's a good man, Edgar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you will restore our family  to greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar? Am I boring you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening, Mother. You fired the maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her when she was through,  she could quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not paying for her impudence.  The whole Negro race is in open revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I could open an investigation.  - Gotten too comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what I said?  I said I could open an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:08.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Palmer called me into a meeting today.  The war against the Bolsheviks has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's insisted that I lead  a new anti-radical division.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you leap like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him this is the greatest  threat our nation has ever faced...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I cannot take the job unless  I feel certain I can be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. But you'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Three thousand a year, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to get new clothes.  You can't look like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have 40 names of suspected radicals  already in only four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have 10,000  by end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:41.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I have my own staff, trusted agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, are you smoking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Doesn't come naturally, Mother.  - Listen to the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,With this new burden,  your nerves could get the better of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to end up like your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go and try one now.  You can put your father in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get ready for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you abandoning me tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's with a typist. She's very organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so. I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:19.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna show her my old card catalog  system at the Library of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Romance her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear a blue tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so handsome in your blue tie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped organize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See, every item is assigned  its own index card...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with its own unique code...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:05.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...indicating the title, author,  location, and topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:09.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What used to take days to locate  now only takes a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. Give me an author  or a topic. Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Indiscretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What era?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Time me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost there, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know I didn't mean  political indiscretion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:08.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'd like,  I can start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How long did I take?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One minute, 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:17.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now imagine if every citizen in this country  were uniquely identifiable...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:21.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...by their own card and number,  say, the pattern on their fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:27.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine how quickly we could find them  if they committed a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all very impressive, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:34.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, would you like to stay here  or would you like to go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:42.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure where you think  this is headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:53.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know we've only known each other  a brief time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you would  make the finest of companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your strength, your character,  your education.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you poking fun at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, no, no. No, no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please, Mr. Hoover, stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it  if you wouldn't share this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with any of the other women  in the typing pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. May I ask what... What...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:33.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What particular flaw  you seem to find in my character?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe that I am a fast  and accurate judge of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gone out three times,  but I don't need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:47.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people do, but I don't.  I see people right off for what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And please, call me Edgar.  It's what my mother uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Edgar?  - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you keep a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Of course. You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:04.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in getting married.  My work comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:14.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then perhaps you would consider  a position as my personal secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:35.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I helped organize that library  just as I did this Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And many said we didn't need either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, innovators  aren't often celebrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:56.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The nitwit Kennedy child  rang his baby buzzer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he'd like a fresh diaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I find out what  the Attorney General needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:09.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want the completed transcripts  of the Los Angeles recordings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When I receive those,  then we'll answer his buzzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, Agent Smith is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He, uh, has some questions  about the Palmer Raids.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I tell him to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Helen, do you like him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have an opinion of him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like him. I trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll set him up in your outer office.  - No. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him a desk in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But in 1920,  how could I protect us from anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I moved to this office,  we were powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We had few federal laws,  no right to carry firearms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Congress liked it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminals ran free, but there was no law  against keeping track of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I made a decision on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:03.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I compiled note cards  and over five thousand names...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and called the one department  in Washington...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that still held a small piece  of untested power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the Department of Labor?  The power to deport, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But only to deport those  who checked two boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:20.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They had to be foreign citizens and they  had to be working to harm our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And they cooperated with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:28.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No one freely shares power  in Washington, D.C., Agent Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:31.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no law  under which you can issue a warrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the arrest of an alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I have certified that  he is subject to deportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Without any evidence,  Mr. Attorney General, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- There exists a due process of law.  - Due process of law?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- What about the threat?  - There might be a threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. There is a threat to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But with no proof of a crime,  there's no cause for deportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be hearing from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But one of their heads was a Mr. Caminetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:06.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was weary of our Justice Department,  but he hated one person even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a revolutionist by nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and as such...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:15.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l claim the right to rebel  and resist invasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...by all means, force included.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Emma Goldman. She was the hero  of the radical movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:27.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could hand Caminetti Emma Goldman,  he would deport her without a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to stop, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:44.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's hard for you to imagine today,  but there was a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:49.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the average American feared  for their safety and survival, Agent Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:54.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In Chicago, a coal strike started  by communist labor shut off all the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Riots followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And on Armistice Day  in Centralia, Washington...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...veterans fresh back from the war  were murdered by radicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The red revolution had arrived on our soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. We can't take them down  one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:20.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll go underground and we'll have  a bomb inside every senator's mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to have a simultaneous raid,  hitting all of them at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:26.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who are "they"?  - You're here to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:30.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen, I want a card on every  radical person in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Against the wall, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:35.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know who, where they're from,  what group, what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who have already committed crimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I care more whether they intend to.  Against the wall, gentlemen, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- How many are on our team?  - Only you four for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have locks installed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Miss Gandy.  That would bring too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is to be alphabetically ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the cards to be broken down  into subjects and categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this system should be easy enough  if explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, finding information  should prove impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:05.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And trust no one,  not even our fellow agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Half our colleagues are on both sides  of the payroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But the crimes we're investigating  aren't crimes, they're ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if your idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Against the wall, gentlemen. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:19.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If your idea is to come into our country  and plot the overthrow of our government...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...then, yes, indeed, that is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Goldman married a U.S. citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The man she married hasn't visited  her once in prison, yet this man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the man she's lived with since her  wedding, he visits nightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens when  we raid this list of yours and find nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:38.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No guns, no bombs,  just innocent people deported.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,From every corner of this nation,  the American people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:45.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...have urged the Attorney General  to do something about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and return the United States  back to peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm happy to send your objections  to Mr. Palmer himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, in the meantime,  expose Miss Goldman's sham marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:57.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you will change that suit of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pardon me, John?  - Your suit, sir, your suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a saloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have respect for yourself,  but, more importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...have respect for this department.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Goldman, are you an anarchist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I decline to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you deny that you are an anarchist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I decline to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:25.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe in the overthrow  of the government of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you advocate the assassination  of public officials?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:39.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This alien has refused to answer questions  pertaining to the charges in the warrant...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:43.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...notwithstanding the fact that  every opportunity was afforded her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend deportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that, we had our precedent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, should I arrange our travel  to Paterson on Valentine's Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:09.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the train to Paterson,  New Jersey, on February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could catch these radicals red-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...then the Labor Department would have  to put them all on boats back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So agents of the Bureau,  alongside local police...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:22.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...began raiding gathering places  of known communist radicals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:25.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...all across this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,These people are armed and violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're prepared to kill to avoid capture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Take one. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are we allowed to use these, sir?  - These are gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no law that prevents us  from using our own weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, grab your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Police! This is a raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going for the window, stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The leaflets matched exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:18.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd solved the bombings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, in the end, we arrested nearly  4000 communist radicals...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:25.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and deported over 500 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:31.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was accomplished against great odds  and at great personal peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:39.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They found the counterfeiting press,  five pistols, two automatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:43.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And in Trenton, they found gunpowder,  copper, brass wire, and batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- A bomb factory.  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:52.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred and twenty arrests in Detroit,  41 in Philadelphia, and 17 here so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:56.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone in the Bureau involved  lost theirjob, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Palmer himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Some did, and there's the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:02.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the bombs stopped,  and peace came.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:05.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The American people had forgotten  there ever was a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:08.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So when political adversaries  attacked Palmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for trying to protect this nation  from communism...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.86,0:24:13.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...our countrymen allowed it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:19.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Because like today, they've forgotten  the bombs, the blood, the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:22.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But why Palmer and not you,  if you orchestrated the raids?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:28.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was 24 years old, Agent Smith.  I was just following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:29.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:34.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we hadn't, you may very well  have been born into a communist state...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.51,0:24:37.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...rather than the country you love today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.39,0:24:39.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Am I right?  - Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.47,0:24:40.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.68,0:24:41.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:44.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:45.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:49.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in a meeting, Mr. Tolson.  I'll be out in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.07,0:24:53.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about your appointment  with the Attorney General, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:58.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Files are not yet completed, Mr. Tolson.  Please go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.91,0:25:00.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:07.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir. I apologize.  I'll finish this chapter tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.04,0:25:10.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Agent Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:23.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Academy, do they tell the story  of how I got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:26.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Uh, you were called into  the new Attorney General's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.15,0:25:30.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Harlan Fiske Stone.  - Yes, sir, Attorney General Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.44,0:25:33.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He called you into his office  and told you to sit down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.40,0:25:35.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, there are over a dozen vacancies  in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.99,0:25:39.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the robbery rates rising,  it would profit the Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:41.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to start filling vacancies  and make recoveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.62,0:25:46.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have files on potential suspects,  and with a congressional hearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:50.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lower the treble, son. You didn't call  this meeting, I did. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.63,0:25:52.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:57.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone you've worked with here is gone.  And there's a reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.01,0:26:03.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This Bureau is of exceedingly bad odor.  Would you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.02,0:26:05.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:08.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, no offense,  you seem to have no social life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.56,0:26:13.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No wife, no girlfriend.  As far as I can tell, no pals at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.53,0:26:18.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That is accurate, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:22.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're shamelessly distracted  by this hodgepodge fingerprinting affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.58,0:26:27.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, it wouldn't be hodgepodge if we could  centralize the prints here, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.66,0:26:29.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a speculative science at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.42,0:26:32.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.25,0:26:35.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do they call you Speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.38,0:26:37.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who calls me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.59,0:26:40.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They all do, behind your back, evidently.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.18,0:26:47.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I gained a reputation for delivering  groceries when I was 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.35,0:26:51.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the fastest in the neighborhood.  It was just a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.27,0:26:53.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's not for the way you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.15,0:26:56.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:27:04.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, I want you to be acting  director of the Bureau of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.08,0:27:11.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the job, Mr. Stone,  but only on certain conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.59,0:27:15.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.25,0:27:21.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bureau must be divorced from politics  and not be a catchall for political hacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.89,0:27:25.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Recruits must be college-educated.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.35,0:27:28.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Appointments must be based on merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.22,0:27:32.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Promotions will be made on proven ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:36.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, well, the Bureau will be  responsible only to you, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.57,0:27:38.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Attorney General.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.03,0:27:44.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't give you the job  under any other conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.70,0:27:48.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all. Good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.54,0:27:52.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.87,0:27:56.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am determined to summarily dismiss  from this Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.09,0:28:00.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...any employee whom I find  indulging in the use of intoxicants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:04.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my belief that when a man  becomes a part of this Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:10.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he must so conduct himself,  both officially and unofficially...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:13.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...as to eliminate even  the slightest possibility of criticism...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.94,0:28:15.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...as to his conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.15,0:28:20.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- And what is your name, sir?  - Agent Williams, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.11,0:28:23.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Pleasure to meet you, Agent Williams.  - You too, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.95,0:28:27.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:28.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Caffrey, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.95,0:28:31.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Your assignment?  - I'm headed to Kansas City...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.45,0:28:34.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to aid in the search  for bank robber Frank Nash, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:36.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, that is dangerous work,  and when you return...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.67,0:28:39.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you will be rewarded for your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.97,0:28:47.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You still fancy facial hair, Agent Stokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:50.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- The ladies appreciate it.  - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.85,0:28:54.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I suppose the ladies' opinions  are more important than the Bureau's?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.35,0:28:55.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.56,0:28:57.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.81,0:29:00.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you are better suited  for the police force...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...than the Bureau of investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:06.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been with the Department and  the Bureau for seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.66,0:29:07.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost as long as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.62,0:29:09.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:14.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with the old Bureau seven years,  and that Bureau is now gone, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.46,0:29:16.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.00,0:29:21.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I quickly dismissed all agents
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.30,0:29:23.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Education, physical fitness...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.09,0:29:26.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, above all, loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.64,0:29:34.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had two made.  Same cut, different pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.19,0:29:39.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And two suits for you.  They'll be delivered on Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.19,0:29:40.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.11,0:29:46.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's platinum...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.66,0:29:51.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...six diamonds and a star sapphire.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.37,0:29:56.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Heh.  - It's absolutely beautiful, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.21,0:29:57.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.21,0:30:03.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told the whole neighborhood  about you. They all know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.88,0:30:07.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I shouldn't,  I've been gaining weight, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:11.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's solid weight. There's nothing wrong  with solid weight on a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.39,0:30:15.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right.  - I'm so incredibly proud of you, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.27,0:30:24.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting an album for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.40,0:30:28.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put everything in it.  This is just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.74,0:30:35.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Johnny Hoover appointed acting director  of the Bureau of investigations."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.29,0:30:36.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.42,0:30:43.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You proud of your uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.27,0:31:00.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:06.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to introduce you. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.07,0:31:10.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.91,0:31:12.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.45,0:31:14.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to introduce you  to Mr. Clyde Tolson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.12,0:31:17.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Graduated from George Washington  University tonight with a law degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.08,0:31:19.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.29,0:31:20.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mr. Tolson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:24.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Hoover. I believe you are  one of our most distinguished alumni.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.96,0:31:28.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I did, yes. L, uh, do have a degree  from the school, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.09,0:31:34.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was admiring your suit, Mr. Tolson.  You should take a lesson, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.72,0:31:37.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir. It's a custom cut,  from Garfinkel's department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:39.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.60,0:31:43.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a card, Mr. Tolson?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.81,0:31:46.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.44,0:31:48.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.82,0:31:50.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good to see you, Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:52.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.20,0:32:00.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well-educated, highly recommended,  willing to guarantee five years service.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.87,0:32:03.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Has a family in New York  and a new baby."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.71,0:32:04.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.38,0:32:07.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The family in New York or the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.67,0:32:11.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, five years is not enough.  We need men willing to dedicate their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.63,0:32:13.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How many is that so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.30,0:32:18.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's 320 denied and 21 interviews.  - Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.72,0:32:22.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we receive an application  from a Mr. Tolson?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.02,0:32:25.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.52,0:32:31.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, his report states  he has confidence, poise...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:33.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...his diction is excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.91,0:32:38.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But although physically fitted for it,  might be displeased with rugged work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.58,0:32:42.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,His only interest is to gain experience  that would benefit a private law practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:32:46.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And he has no interest in being here  for any period of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.79,0:32:49.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...which would render  employment speculative.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.46,0:32:51.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.05,0:32:54.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He did receive  a letter of recommendation...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.93,0:32:58.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...from the executive assistant  of the Secretary of War.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:01.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fantastic, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.18,0:33:08.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It mentions here that Mr. Tolson  showed no particular interest in women.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.73,0:33:16.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, some of our best agents excel  because they have no family encumbrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:20.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right. Set up an interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.54,0:33:25.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what the problem is,  Miss Gandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.75,0:33:28.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,These men, they don't...  They don't look up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.88,0:33:30.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.21,0:33:35.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean figuratively.  I mean they don't look up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:39.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you could conduct the entire  interview from behind your desk...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.43,0:33:44.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...instead of walking about the office,  I could correct that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.81,0:33:46.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.73,0:33:52.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, suppose I had information  on someone in a position of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.11,0:33:56.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...harmful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.11,0:33:59.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes against my nature  to destroy such information...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.87,0:34:02.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't trust it  in the general files either.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.95,0:34:06.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I trust it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.79,0:34:10.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to create a confidential file?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.79,0:34:13.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.67,0:34:16.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.89,0:34:23.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Information is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.26,0:34:26.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It protected us from the communists  in 1919...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.39,0:34:30.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and since has been vigilantly collected,  organized, and maintained by our FBl.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.73,0:34:35.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Attorney General Kennedy's Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.74,0:34:44.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you always have this fireplace  or did you have it put in?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.54,0:34:45.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.75,0:34:48.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing with wiretaps  in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.54,0:34:53.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked that I pursue this  organized crime element, Mr. Kennedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.67,0:34:56.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I did so, sir, with diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.84,0:34:59.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you use the fireplace?  - Rarely.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.30,0:35:00.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else has heard the recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.84,0:35:05.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have filed the matter  personal and confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.68,0:35:07.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only person with access to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:11.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, I asked you to pursue  a real threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:15.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you've publicly denied  the existence of organized crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.86,0:35:18.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now this gross display  of intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.36,0:35:22.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Attorney General,  I was only following orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.20,0:35:24.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We bugged the basement of a home  in Los Angeles...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.62,0:35:27.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that was a known gathering place  for lawbreakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.70,0:35:32.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How was I to know that an East German  communist would be down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.29,0:35:36.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...having sex with your brother,  the President of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.05,0:35:40.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not shoot the messenger, sir.  I am here to protect you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.80,0:35:42.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.43,0:35:47.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.06,0:35:52.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If this information were to go public...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.90,0:35:57.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would create widespread distrust  in your brother's leadership capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.19,0:36:01.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And above all else, I hold the well-being  of our country paramount.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.90,0:36:04.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So how may I help you, Mr. Hoover?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.70,0:36:09.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I am to pursue the elements  that you consider a threat...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.75,0:36:13.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l humbly request that you allow me  the same power and access...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.58,0:36:16.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to follow the groups that I see  as an immediate threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.59,0:36:18.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not 1920 anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.72,0:36:22.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know who Stanley Levinson is, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:25.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.10,0:36:30.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A white, communist lawyer  organizing at the highest levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.27,0:36:32.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...including the SCLC.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.19,0:36:33.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, their group is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:36.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They are entirely self-serving...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:40.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and their leadership is openly critical  of this department here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.28,0:36:42.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read the memos that I sent?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.20,0:36:44.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I can't say that I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.45,0:36:48.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It says right here, Mr. Kennedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.62,0:36:50.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They claim we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:53.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,..."unable to get convictions in even  the worst, most heinous crimes..."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:36:57.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that we have "faltered under  the pressure, complexities...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.38,0:36:59.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and responsibilities of our office,"  in print.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.84,0:37:03.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Right here in "The Washington Post."  - You can't bear a little criticism?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.72,0:37:05.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it depends on what their aim is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.14,0:37:08.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They are gaining considerable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.47,0:37:11.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Their priorities are singularly focused  on their own issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.52,0:37:13.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They are trying to incite revolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:17.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, they sound more critical  of your office than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.19,0:37:21.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a new face to communism,  Edgar, and this isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.15,0:37:25.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Communism is a foreign threat now,  not domestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.16,0:37:31.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kennedy,  before you were even born...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.83,0:37:36.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l heard that very same argument  from a Mr. Mitchell Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.33,0:37:39.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what it took  to change his mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.17,0:37:41.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.84,0:37:45.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If he would have sat in his rocking chair  five more minutes in 1919...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:49.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'd have been lucky enough  to find an intact index finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:53.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I do not want that to happen  to you or your brother, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.02,0:37:57.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason  we both can't get what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:38:01.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We can wage a war on two fronts, sir.  You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.90,0:38:06.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go now, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.70,0:38:10.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.12,0:38:14.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the transcripts here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:18.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.80,0:38:26.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and feel free and share them  with your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.88,0:38:33.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and let him know that I have  a copy of my own in safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.87,0:38:52.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Unh.  - Your 4:00 is here, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.12,0:38:55.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Gandy.  Send him right in, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.87,0:39:03.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have a seat, Mr. Tolson.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.38,0:39:07.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Hoover, thank you for this opportunity.  - Yes. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.26,0:39:09.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have a seat.  - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.76,0:39:13.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There were several problems  with your application, Mr. Tolson...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.39,0:39:16.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...not the least of which is the fact  that you did not show...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.47,0:39:18.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the proper requirement to the Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.44,0:39:24.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...nor the proper dedication  to protecting the American people...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.23,0:39:25.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the American way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.44,0:39:27.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,May I remind you  that this is not a platform...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.03,0:39:31.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to a fatter paycheck in private practice,  Mr. Tolson?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:38.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something the matter,  Mr. Tolson?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.45,0:39:40.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.62,0:39:43.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ls exercise a requirement  for all agents, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.88,0:39:49.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. All our agents need to be  in top physical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.97,0:39:54.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We must outsmart and outmatch  the public enemy at every turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.47,0:39:56.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:59.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh, what routine do you do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.64,0:40:03.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Push-ups, sit-ups, and squatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:05.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.94,0:40:07.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to fix the curtain?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.40,0:40:09.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps I could open a window.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.15,0:40:12.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I always prefer  a little bit of air after exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.78,0:40:14.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.49,0:40:16.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If it would please you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:21.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, sir, where I may fall short  in terms of resume...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.12,0:40:25.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l apparently far exceed  the rest in terms of honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.92,0:40:28.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie to get this appointment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.75,0:40:31.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the rest, yes,  I would like to start a practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.38,0:40:37.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I could be persuaded otherwise  if the right opportunities were to arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.51,0:40:40.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.56,0:40:44.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fair enough, Mr. Tolson.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.19,0:40:47.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.29,0:41:02.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,These sleeves seem to be  the correct length.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.46,0:41:04.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you two tie options.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:06.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This one is a bit more fashion-forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.54,0:41:09.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it would complement this suit  and cut and fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.25,0:41:10.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too loud, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:13.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Too loud? Okay, which is why  I found this one, the backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.84,0:41:18.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's a bit more directorial, a little bit more...  - It's a little bit more reserved, I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.72,0:41:22.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this as a second option, please.  Thank you, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.73,0:41:26.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Mr. John Hoover?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:28.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.36,0:41:32.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there's a Mr. John Hoover  whose credit has gone bad with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.65,0:41:34.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That would appear to be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.36,0:41:36.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not me, sir, on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.16,0:41:41.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother calls me Edgar, my niece calls  me J.E., and I sign John E., not John.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.12,0:41:45.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sir, if you're a friend  of Mr. Tolson's...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.04,0:41:49.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...just choose one name and reapply.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.75,0:41:51.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.21,0:41:53.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.89,0:42:04.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.64,0:42:07.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.06,0:42:12.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover,  there's been a massacre in Kansas City.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.03,0:42:16.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One of our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.74,0:42:20.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Agent Caffrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.33,0:42:22.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.29,0:42:26.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,By 1930, the communist threat  had been beaten back...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.37,0:42:30.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the Depression had hit  and there was a new threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.79,0:42:33.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The bank robber, the car thief,  and the kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.67,0:42:38.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But, unfortunately, as with communism,  America didn't react with scorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.13,0:42:42.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave the American gangster  admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.39,0:42:44.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And the defiance by desperate,  armed criminals...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:49.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the forces of society and civilization  can no longer be ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.35,0:42:53.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bugs Moran and Al Capone  top the list of public enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.40,0:42:56.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Look around you.  They could be anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.69,0:43:01.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,May I remind you that the Bureau of  Investigation seeks to be your protector.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:04.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to you. It is as close to you  as your nearest telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.04,0:43:07.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And with your help...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.29,0:43:11.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Warner Bros. Presents
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.63,0:43:13.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Public Enemy."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.04,0:43:17.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,James Cagney plays  public enemy number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.01,0:43:20.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why, you.  - Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.22,0:43:24.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go with that wishing stuff again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.43,0:43:26.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you found someone  you like better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.18,0:43:31.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming soon to your neighborhood theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.81,0:43:33.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.73,0:43:39.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That summer, a single crime opened  the door to set things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.07,0:43:42.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that was, Mr. Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.99,0:43:44.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sir, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:47.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the most famous man  of the 20th Century thus far?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.83,0:43:50.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe McCarthy, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.58,0:43:54.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. McCarthy was an opportunist...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.09,0:43:57.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...not a patriot, Mr. Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.88,0:44:04.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the most famous man  of the 20th Century thus far?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.47,0:44:07.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The most famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.77,0:44:09.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ls that you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.40,0:44:20.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose his notoriety  depends on the field that he is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.90,0:44:24.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,His field was in the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.24,0:44:27.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then Charles Lindbergh, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.51,0:44:41.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.72,0:44:44.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Charles Lindbergh's  baby has been kidnapped from his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.84,0:44:48.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Send officers from Trenton.  I'll be on the first train.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.56,0:44:54.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.77,0:45:00.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Charles Lindbergh...  Lindbergh's baby's been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.61,0:45:03.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.07,0:45:07.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be brought home alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:10.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.58,0:45:15.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.21,0:45:22.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When we arrived at  Mr. Lindbergh's home that morning in 1932...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.09,0:45:26.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...we began an investigation that would  forever change our Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.59,0:45:29.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning we've heard from  the Pennsylvania Railroad, Will Rogers...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.06,0:45:32.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...President Hoover,  Governor Roosevelt, Customs...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:34.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the U.S. Mail, and the Boy Scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.06,0:45:36.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you. Get off of that dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.81,0:45:39.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trampling evidence.  Immediately! Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.65,0:45:42.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing there. We checked.  No defined footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.78,0:45:44.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he was wearing fabric  on his shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.15,0:45:47.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think the size  could've held some value?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.99,0:45:51.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How did he get up there? Are there  marks on the window and wall as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.49,0:45:53.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A ladder.  We found it 100 yards away.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.62,0:45:55.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We moved it inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.25,0:45:56.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You moved it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.58,0:45:58.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:46:02.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mr. Schwarzkopf.  You have contaminated the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.50,0:46:04.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get your boots off this property.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.76,0:46:07.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And what right do you have  to be here, Mister, uh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.22,0:46:09.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,J. Edgar Hoover,  director of the Bureau of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.01,0:46:13.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been sent by President Hoover  to ensure the investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.18,0:46:16.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The president has authorized access  to all documents and evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.44,0:46:20.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, you're free to observe,  but New Jersey's not the president's domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.44,0:46:24.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is Mr. Lindbergh?  I'd like to hear his opinion on the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.19,0:46:26.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Lindbergh's around back.  - After you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.45,0:46:28.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been up all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.28,0:46:31.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lindbergh himself  came down to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.49,0:46:36.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He shook my hand and expressed his  gratitude and faith in our young Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.29,0:46:39.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell five feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.46,0:46:40.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.84,0:46:45.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper, with the child in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.47,0:46:48.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's speculation, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.34,0:46:53.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lindbergh, sir, if the ladder had split  while the person was on their way up...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.18,0:46:55.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...it would have collapsed.  You see, it was a miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.14,0:47:00.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was meant to bear the weight of a man,  but not the weight of a man and child.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.85,0:47:01.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We have other theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:04.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the ransom note?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.98,0:47:06.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.82,0:47:10.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are touching that  with your bare hands as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.53,0:47:11.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.74,0:47:15.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There are none of those finger imprints  that you fancy so valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.29,0:47:17.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hand it over, Mr. Schwarzkopf.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.25,0:47:19.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Colonel Schwarzkopf.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.38,0:47:25.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Have 50,000 dollars ready,"  spelled R-E-D-Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.38,0:47:29.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"We will inform you where,"  spelled W-E-R-E, "to deliver the money"...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.17,0:47:30.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...spelled M-O-N-Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.68,0:47:34.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"We warn you for making anything public  or for notify the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.01,0:47:39.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Indication for all letters are signature,"  S-I-N-G, "singnature."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.69,0:47:42.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Three holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.86,0:47:45.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want this letter and the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.11,0:47:48.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No jurisdiction.  I've showed what you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.44,0:47:50.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's time for you to go.  - Mr. Lindbergh, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.03,0:47:54.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, thank you. As you can see,  we have everything under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.58,0:47:56.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.54,0:47:58.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your time, Mr. Lindbergh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.04,0:48:01.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.84,0:48:12.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, I'm afraid for his boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.34,0:48:15.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He trusts the local police more than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.85,0:48:17.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks we're all fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.47,0:48:21.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll go around them too.  He's going to bargain with the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.56,0:48:26.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President Hoover called me the morning  the child was taken...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.77,0:48:29.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and asked me to do whatever was  in my power to solve this crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.11,0:48:33.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you know what all the power  of the Bureau means...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.24,0:48:38.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...without federal laws, without arms,  without the ability to make arrests?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.37,0:48:40.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.37,0:48:43.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Chairman, I urge passage  of the Lindbergh Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.12,0:48:46.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...making kidnapping a federal offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.67,0:48:50.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To immediately deliver all the fingerprints  in this country to my office...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.84,0:48:53.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that we may create a central file.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.18,0:48:56.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To help arm our agents  so that they have a fighting chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.51,0:49:00.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...against the submachine guns of some  of the most dangerous characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.52,0:49:02.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the history of American criminality.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.64,0:49:06.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I urge you to do this  in the name of Little Lindy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.23,0:49:09.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if he can be taken,  then what child is safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.69,0:49:15.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if we cannot aid in his safe return,  then what use are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.01,0:49:40.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Every fingerprint from the local authorities...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.31,0:49:44.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...across the country began flowing in.  Finally, we had a centralized system.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.69,0:49:46.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.65,0:49:50.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The last of the fingerprints came in  from Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.07,0:49:57.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know our new president has scheduled  a meeting with me, Miss Gandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.57,0:50:02.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that there are talks  of reorganizing the Bureau?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.37,0:50:05.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've heard similar whispers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.17,0:50:08.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.96,0:50:15.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, do you remember that file  we created on his wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.26,0:50:16.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Roosevelt?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.01,0:50:18.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.76,0:50:20.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you make a copy for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.76,0:50:23.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.27,0:50:27.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.76,0:51:03.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lindbergh hired criminals to find his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.22,0:51:06.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Off the desk now, Agent Garrison,  follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.68,0:51:07.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.89,0:51:10.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He even got an offer from Al Capone  to help pay the ransom money...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.15,0:51:15.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, in the end, he employed an eccentric  by the name of John Condon...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.23,0:51:19.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...who placed a newspaper ad to act  as a go-between with the kidnappers.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.65,0:51:22.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, was Condon a criminal too?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.24,0:51:25.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He most certainly wasn't  an agent of the law, Mr. Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.79,0:51:27.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.46,0:51:30.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So a mother may have her baby again.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.54,0:51:34.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you may know that the  American people are grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.84,0:51:37.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the honor bestowed upon them  by your pluck and daring.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.13,0:51:42.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And how do we know the kidnapper is the  same that wrote the letters that you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.60,0:51:47.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The symbol, uh, matches  the original letter's symbol, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.69,0:51:53.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mr. Lindbergh?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.69,0:51:59.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In a moment of thoughtlessness...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.86,0:52:02.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l showed the symbol  to some other men...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.20,0:52:05.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm not sure  that they were trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.37,0:52:08.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure anyone is trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.00,0:52:11.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be having your letters analyzed...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.04,0:52:15.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make sure that they  are from the same author.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.21,0:52:19.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And while Mr. Lindbergh  placed his faith in hoodlums...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.71,0:52:23.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...we began cultivating the one thing  criminals couldn't fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.39,0:52:25.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with all the guns in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.22,0:52:29.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, please leave this room.  Clear all these tables. Time to go, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.52,0:52:30.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can we smoke, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.85,0:52:32.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my concern. Out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.60,0:52:35.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. Osborne, tell us what you need.  - Uh, bright lights, a microscope...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.90,0:52:38.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...measuring instruments,  magnifying glasses. A, uh, projector.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.57,0:52:41.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the full resources of the Bureau.  Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.70,0:52:43.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper samples from  every regional manufacturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.99,0:52:47.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Osborne, this is Mr. Tolson.  Supply Mr. Osborne whatever he needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.78,0:52:51.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to conclude without a doubt that  these letters came from the same author.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.96,0:52:53.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.88,0:52:57.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, please. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.67,0:53:02.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Should we tell the attorney general?  - So he can say no a third time?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.05,0:53:06.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Just post a sign, like this one.  - What would you like it to say, "keep out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.97,0:53:09.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Bureau of investigations  Technical Laboratory."
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.72,0:53:13.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have it carved and nailed to the wall.  If he wants it gone, he'll have to tear it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.89,0:53:16.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time we at least have one thing  the bad guys don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.06,0:53:18.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Decorating skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.27,0:53:19.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Science, Clyde. Science.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.98,0:53:24.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, the ink is different,  but the handwriting is a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.28,0:53:29.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever Mr. Condon is corresponding with  is the person who wrote the original note.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.24,0:53:31.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Or Condon wrote all the notes himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.37,0:53:34.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lindbergh is planning on using  Condon to deliver the ransom.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.16,0:53:36.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- May have already happened.  - Call the internal Revenue Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.79,0:53:40.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them to Lindbergh's home.  I insist that all those bills be marked.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:41.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.05,0:53:44.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ls that all, Mr. Hoover?  I have a 2:30 p.m. class to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.05,0:53:47.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't.  Consider your pay doubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.30,0:53:52.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You work for your country now,  Mr. Osborne. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.73,0:53:56.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.57,0:54:08.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotted the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.99,0:54:11.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring the money till I see the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.42,0:54:19.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you there's no police.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.75,0:54:22.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.59,0:54:32.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.27,0:54:35.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.14,0:54:37.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If they catch me, they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.06,0:54:40.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they only want the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.61,0:54:43.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll give me 30 years if I'm caught.  They could burn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.15,0:54:45.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.78,0:54:46.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.03,0:54:48.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only the messenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.24,0:54:50.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.16,0:54:52.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the baby is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.24,0:54:55.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I burn if the baby is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.54,0:55:00.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we be meeting  if the baby was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.21,0:55:03.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Place another ad in the paper  when you have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.88,0:55:14.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So if a ransom had to be paid,  we needed those bills traced.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.39,0:55:18.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought in the lRS, and, for his  own good, we had to force his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.73,0:55:21.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought gold notes were going  out of circulation, Mr. lrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.73,0:55:23.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.23,0:55:25.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make these bills more identifiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.28,0:55:27.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need for the money.  I just want my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.40,0:55:32.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just about your son,  Mr. Lindbergh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.53,0:55:36.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If these kidnappers go free,  then no child in this country will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.58,0:55:41.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've assembled a 26-man team,  headed by Special Agent Sisk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.54,0:55:45.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they find out you're involved,  I may never see my son again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.55,0:55:49.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lindbergh, sir,  we will not pursue a single lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.63,0:55:51.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...until your child is safe  in his mother's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.09,0:55:54.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my word, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.94,0:56:05.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapping of  Charles A. Lindbergh, Jr., was a tragedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.11,0:56:08.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...not only to Colonel and Mrs. Lindbergh,  but to the nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.86,0:56:11.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,His abduction from his Hopewell home  was a challenge to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.11,0:56:14.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This ladder, the only clue  to the kidnapping, was homemade.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.03,0:56:17.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let the developments in the Lindbergh  case start a new drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.12,0:56:21.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to wipe out the stain,  not only of that wanton kidnapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.16,0:56:24.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but of all kidnapping and crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.80,0:56:28.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.21,0:56:32.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Give your word not to open for six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.47,0:56:35.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.77,0:56:45.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I talked him out of 20,000 dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.11,0:56:49.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd prefer him happy than save the money.  I don't want to upset him.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.57,0:56:51.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.99,0:56:54.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised not to open this for six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.74,0:56:57.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You gave your word, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.83,0:57:03.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"The boy is on boat Nelly.  It is a small boat, 28 feet long.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.46,0:57:06.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Two persons are on the boat.  They are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.67,0:57:11.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find the boat between Horseneck's  Beach and Gay Head near Elizabeth island."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.84,0:57:13.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nantucket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.85,0:57:19.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What was in the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.22,0:57:20.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.77,0:57:23.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lindbergh didn't trust us.  He wanted to do things his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.60,0:57:27.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And who can blame him?  No one respected us at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.36,0:57:29.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, we've been calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.23,0:57:30.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.45,0:57:35.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go, Agent Garrison. Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.53,0:57:39.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The Attorney General has authorized  your wiretaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.87,0:57:41.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.54,0:57:46.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, are you sure about this?  Once you do this, Edgar, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.88,0:57:50.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When I prove myself correct, we will have  saved this country another revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.84,0:57:52.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,History will remember that, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.67,0:57:53.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you are wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.05,0:57:57.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...history will remember it as an  illegal move over a petty grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.55,0:58:00.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you consider our reputation petty,  Mr. Tolson?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.68,0:58:03.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- No, I...  - Then order the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.81,0:58:08.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Can we discuss this over dinner?  - After you've ordered the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.44,0:58:11.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.58,0:58:26.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The director's on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.81,0:58:51.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ahem.  - After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.80,0:59:15.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.80,0:59:24.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Harvey's Restaurant, sir?  - No, to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.44,0:59:37.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the midst  of a Great Depression...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.69,0:59:40.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and breaths away from  history's worst war.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.66,0:59:44.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We needed more power to protect,  but, as with every new president...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.66,0:59:49.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...this Bureau's future and my very job  was being drawn into question.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.33,0:59:52.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- The president is ready to see you now.  - Alrighty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.18,1:00:03.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in. Have a seat, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.51,1:00:09.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same dance each time.  They make me wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.81,1:00:14.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They imagine I'm sweating, that they're  gonna show me who's boss, I play along.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.02,1:00:16.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.82,1:00:18.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And then did you show him  the transcript?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.86,1:00:21.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He didn't want to read it.  That was unique.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.99,1:00:24.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted me to tell him about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.37,1:00:26.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What, how you came across it?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.24,1:00:30.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I explained to him up front  we never expected to find Mrs. Roosevelt...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.54,1:00:32.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the bedroom of  a known communist agitator...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.12,1:00:36.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...much less having what sounded like  an intimate moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.71,1:00:39.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That I needed his advice  on how to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.88,1:00:42.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to let him know he had an ally.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.51,1:00:44.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he had a chance  to ask you to resign.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.68,1:00:45.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.10,1:00:48.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was finished,  he simply pushed the file aside...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.06,1:00:53.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...as if he was unconcerned with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.48,1:00:57.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, the President of the United States  is afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.48,1:01:00.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What, he's afraid of you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.23,1:01:04.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of a potential invasion from abroad.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.99,1:01:07.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have two glasses  of your finest champagne.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.74,1:01:09.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.08,1:01:12.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ahem.  - You're drinking now?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.75,1:01:14.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating, Clyde,  we're celebrating.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.54,1:01:18.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I feel I could trust you  with anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.29,1:01:19.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.30,1:01:24.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The president signed a secret order...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.13,1:01:27.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...granting me increased power  of surveillance...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.60,1:01:32.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...secret surveillance of communists  and radicals, without warrant.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.06,1:01:34.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ls that legal?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.27,1:01:36.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you need  to bend the rules a little...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.85,1:01:39.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to keep  your country safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.44,1:01:43.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And to make sure I hadn't heard it wrong,  I clarified this with Secretary of State Hull.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.07,1:01:48.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said, and I quote, "You go ahead  and investigate those cocksuckers."
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.66,1:01:52.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Vulgar.  - Hmm, agreed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.12,1:01:56.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.46,1:01:59.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've been meaning  to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.17,1:02:01.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.30,1:02:05.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need someone who understands  what's at stake here...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.97,1:02:07.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.43,1:02:09.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who I can trust...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.14,1:02:12.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...an associate director of the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.14,1:02:16.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've only been in your  current position for, what, 12 months now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.77,1:02:18.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, almost 18 now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.81,1:02:21.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're missing my point, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.40,1:02:23.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be my number-two man.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.20,1:02:29.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not much for the spotlight, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.49,1:02:34.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.79,1:02:36.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand? I need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.67,1:02:41.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On one condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.25,1:02:45.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day or bad,  whether we agree or disagree...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.42,1:02:49.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...we never miss a lunch  or a dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.18,1:02:52.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would have it no other way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.19,1:03:04.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pull over.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.65,1:03:07.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Only a half a mile to Mount Rose.  - Can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.06,1:03:39.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Orville!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.95,1:03:57.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the child's body  was found just within sight...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.58,1:03:59.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...of Mr. Lindbergh's home.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.08,1:04:02.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The body was blackened...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.08,1:04:06.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the left leg missing  from the knee down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.67,1:04:09.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a visible fracture on the skull.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.09,1:04:13.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd suffered a violent blow to the head.  I told them months ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.43,1:04:17.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've fallen on the way down,  with the baby in his arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.77,1:04:21.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the sinners, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.19,1:04:29.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We tolerated lawlessness in the land  until it grew to diabolical proportions.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.78,1:04:33.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The baby's blood is on all our hands,  Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.45,1:04:37.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On your hands, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.79,1:04:45.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.51,1:05:00.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Six weeks after the kidnapping...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.52,1:05:02.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Congress passed the Lindbergh Law...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.52,1:05:05.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...making kidnapping a federal offense.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.44,1:05:09.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The right to make arrests followed  and the right to bear arms.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.48,1:05:13.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So I continued collecting the finest  scientific minds in the country.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.78,1:05:20.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He claims to be the world expert  on wood analysis.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.54,1:05:24.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to be the expert if you're the  only person in the world with any interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.58,1:05:26.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He does claim he can tell  as much from a cut of wood...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.08,1:05:29.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a doctor can from an autopsy.  - Ah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.42,1:05:31.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He has, um, social difficulties.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.01,1:05:34.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He is mentally ill, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.34,1:05:37.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's only as mad as you are. Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.51,1:05:41.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This was supposed to be temporary,  Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.43,1:05:43.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want your Sherlock Holmes  playing time...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.77,1:05:46.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you suggest we go, sir, where?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.52,1:05:48.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you take your case  to Congress.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.61,1:05:49.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, sir. Have it your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.07,1:05:54.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell people we could not solve the case  because we could not afford laboratories...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.15,1:05:58.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Attorney General  wouldn't allow us to use his lounge.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.24,1:06:01.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Now get your science fair project  out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.87,1:06:03.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.21,1:06:07.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, keep working.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.46,1:06:10.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tolson,  let's get the president on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.88,1:06:17.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The depravations of vicious outlaws, roving  from state to state like packs of wolves...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.93,1:06:20.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...amounts to an actual  armed invasion of America.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.76,1:06:24.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We must outsmart and outwit the criminal,  foreign and domestic.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.68,1:06:28.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They have chemists building bombs.  We need chemists tracing their efforts.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.81,1:06:31.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We must have the most advanced  force in the world...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.73,1:06:34.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we are to have the safest nation  on earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.32,1:06:37.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And, please, gentlemen, let us not  for a moment lose sight of our goals:
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.07,1:06:39.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To protect the honest citizen...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.70,1:06:43.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to teach the criminal that  regardless of his subterfuges...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.74,1:06:46.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...his twisting, his squirming  and slimy wriggling...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.50,1:06:49.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he cannot escape the one  inexorable rule of law enforcement...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.96,1:06:51.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you can't get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.09,1:06:53.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.92,1:06:54.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.09,1:07:01.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But your agency is already one of the most  well-funded in Washington, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.18,1:07:02.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is true, sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.85,1:07:06.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but our car and bank robbery recoveries  totaled 6.5 million last year...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.93,1:07:09.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and our budget is only,  well, two million.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.56,1:07:13.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike other departments in Washington,  we actually run a profit.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.28,1:07:17.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot quantify  the value of our successes...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.95,1:07:22.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the hoodlums Pretty Boy Floyd,  Baby Face Nelson, Machine Gun Kelly...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.20,1:07:24.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and other hoodlums of that nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.49,1:07:30.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, is it true that you spend  the Bureau's money on advertising?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.92,1:07:36.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not permitted to engage  in advertising of any kind, sir. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.46,1:07:40.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But you take part, for instance, in the  making of radio shows and comic books.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.14,1:07:43.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've listened to several  of these G-Men programs.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.80,1:07:48.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your picture seems to be shown  in conjunction with them quite frequently.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.31,1:07:53.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We declined emphatically to lend  any form of endorsement...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.36,1:07:58.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...had nothing to do with their production,  furnished no advice, technical or otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.24,1:08:01.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the very advertisement says  that broadcasts were...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.61,1:08:05.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,..."true reflections,  as contained in the official records...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.99,1:08:09.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...based on actual cases from the files  of the Federal Bureau of investigation...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.91,1:08:11.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Saturday night at 8:00."
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.13,1:08:15.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover,  what are your exact qualifications...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.84,1:08:18.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for your position of leadership  in this Bureau?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.51,1:08:19.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My qualifications, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.92,1:08:23.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nineteen years with the  Department of Justice. Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.97,1:08:25.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Twelve as director.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.68,1:08:29.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In all that time,  you ever make an arrest yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.02,1:08:35.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made investigations.  I administer several cases at once.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.61,1:08:38.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's not what I asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.19,1:08:42.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The comic books show you with a machine  gun, making arrests. Ls that just fiction?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.83,1:08:52.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I am responsible for  thousands of arrests, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.58,1:08:56.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So you admit it is pure fiction.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.46,1:09:02.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it wasn't you who hunted down  and captured John Dillinger at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.51,1:09:05.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Agent Purvis. Ls that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.39,1:09:10.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in charge of all of those  investigations...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.85,1:09:14.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but, no, sir, I have not personally  made an arrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.24,1:09:23.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Any other questions, gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.24,1:09:26.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.87,1:09:31.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Put those away.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.42,1:09:37.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that didn't go well.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.00,1:09:40.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We spend our lives working  and we get a political attack?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.92,1:09:44.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he expect, crimes to go  unsolved? Why is he fighting me?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.59,1:09:46.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to start a file  on Senator McKellar.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.84,1:09:48.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want four agents on him at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.80,1:09:51.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what's in his trash,  photograph him at dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.93,1:09:55.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the car. You can walk back.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.77,1:09:58.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We have lunch.  We don't miss lunch, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.44,1:10:00.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You pulled away from me in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.44,1:10:03.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You perjured yourself, Edgar,  and the lie was an easily provable one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.94,1:10:05.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling  how much worse it could've been.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.11,1:10:09.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Find Agent Purvis. He is to be  demoted immediately or, better yet, fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.16,1:10:12.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing the man who killed John Dillinger  would be a PR disaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.00,1:10:15.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he is to spend the rest of his career  behind a desk.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.41,1:10:19.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he'd like to keep that job,  he'd best stay out of the papers. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.22,1:10:32.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who I can trust anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.89,1:10:34.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.48,1:10:38.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Only you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.65,1:10:43.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all I have to keep me safe,  you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.19,1:10:46.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Mother,  let me take you to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.57,1:10:49.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple examination isn't unholy, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.49,1:10:52.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.83,1:10:55.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.83,1:11:01.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Faith, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.84,1:11:03.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Faith.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.84,1:11:07.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wilt like a little flower.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.34,1:11:09.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Be strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.76,1:11:12.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.64,1:11:19.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.11,1:11:28.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,if what Congress valued more  than wits and brains was muscle...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.32,1:11:31.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...if what they hungered for  was an armed American hero...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.57,1:11:35.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...then I was willing to risk my very life  and give them both.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.54,1:11:36.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.87,1:11:38.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.33,1:11:39.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, government agents!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.51,1:11:56.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The arrest is mine to make!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.39,1:11:58.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.56,1:12:01.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Karpis, you are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.23,1:12:06.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover himself.  I'm gonna be famous.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.90,1:12:08.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the handcuffs on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.66,1:12:15.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Mr. Mahan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.74,1:12:18.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.87,1:12:22.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.72,1:12:37.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Brunette, you are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.26,1:12:41.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Alvin Karpis said he couldn't be taken alive,  but we took him without firing a shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.73,1:12:45.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And let me tell you, he shook all over.  His voice, his hands, and his knees.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.73,1:12:48.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You arrested Harry Campbell in Toledo  and Brunette in Manhattan?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.94,1:12:50.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And William Mahan in California.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.65,1:12:53.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me clarify  without a shadow of a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.32,1:12:55.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...this was a "we" job, not an "I" job.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.71,1:13:05.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, look at this.  We made the Post Toasties box.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.46,1:13:09.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Melvin Purvis,  the FBl agent that caught Dillinger."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.51,1:13:12.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Write the cereal-maker.  Let them know...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.22,1:13:15.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. "Junior G-Man." Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.80,1:13:20.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them they ought to print any further  boxes to read "former agent of the FBl."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.64,1:13:23.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down, Clyde.  I'm gonna read something.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.98,1:13:29.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Only eight more days.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.94,1:13:32.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny how even the dearest face  will fade away in time.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.15,1:13:34.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Most clearly, I remember your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.03,1:13:39.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a sort of teasing smile in them,  and the feeling of that soft spot...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.41,1:13:43.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...just northeast of the corner  of your mouth against my lips."
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.16,1:13:44.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.75,1:13:46.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a letter from Lorena Hickok...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.54,1:13:50.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the White House reporter with  the bad breath, to Mrs. Roosevelt.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.30,1:13:54.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. What are you gonna do with it?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.34,1:13:56.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I accused her  of having an affair with a man...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.09,1:14:00.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Old Horse Face is having  an affair with Mrs. Bat Breath!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.35,1:14:03.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- A woman! Can you believe it?  - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.19,1:14:11.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me, Mr. Hoover.  They'd like to see you in the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.53,1:14:14.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss Gandy. You tell them  I'll be there in one minute. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.03,1:14:16.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get to this later.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.82,1:14:21.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of horses, Clyde,  I'm going to Del Mar this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.33,1:14:24.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of taking  a quick vacation...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.50,1:14:27.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and, well,  I thought you'd like to join me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.83,1:14:30.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never been  to the horse races, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.21,1:14:31.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.46,1:14:36.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And between me and you, when I lose,  the track, they actually cover the losses.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.88,1:14:40.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- So, what happens if you win?  - They still pay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.72,1:14:41.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then where's the thrill?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.97,1:14:45.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sun that falls on the stands,  the hotel rooms, the service...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.02,1:14:49.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the restaurants, but, most of all,  Clyde, it's the company.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.06,1:14:53.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Come with me.  - I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.32,1:14:56.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Fantastic. I'll have Miss Gandy  make all the arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.65,1:14:59.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't go now. But maybe  in a couple months after I've saved up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.07,1:15:03.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's completely covered, Clyde.  - Edgar, I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.58,1:15:07.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you've done so much for me,  for this Bureau. Consider it a thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.00,1:15:10.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that I'd feel comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.34,1:15:14.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a suite with adjoining rooms...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.38,1:15:17.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...rather than having us stay separate.  That'll be savings enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.34,1:15:19.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.18,1:15:21.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have for me, Mr. Koehler?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.10,1:15:25.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as you can see, ahem,  there are several kinds of wood here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.60,1:15:29.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pine, birch, fir, and, if you look closely,  you will see...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.10,1:15:31.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you.  - Mr. Tolson.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.44,1:15:35.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That each has its own internal markings,  rings and knots...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.28,1:15:39.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and its own external markings from  the machinery used to mill the raw timber...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.28,1:15:42.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and these that mark the tools  used to build the ladder.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.87,1:15:46.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is, how does this help us  identify the kidnappers, Mr. Koehler?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.12,1:15:48.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more money, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.91,1:15:51.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- More money, sir, for what?  - Postage.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.58,1:15:54.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to write every mill  on the East Coast...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.25,1:15:57.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and see if their blades  match these marks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.80,1:15:59.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.63,1:16:02.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a report from each mill  and a map tracking all leads.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.97,1:16:06.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I get back from New York,  I want something to report.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.47,1:16:07.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.65,1:16:18.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the communist radicals  before them...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.99,1:16:20.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the gangster fell from favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.65,1:16:24.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, finally, children dreamed  of joining the FBl.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.08,1:16:35.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On your feet. On your feet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.92,1:16:40.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.76,1:16:43.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking his shower. Any message?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.09,1:16:46.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There ain't any shower there, copper.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.69,1:17:00.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Temple!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.03,1:17:04.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, I was wondering  if you would join my police force.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.91,1:17:06.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, yes, Miss Temple.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.45,1:17:10.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you agree to be an honorary G-Woman,  and give me one little kiss.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.50,1:17:14.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if your wife would approve,  Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:17.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you see,  I still live with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.88,1:17:21.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.63,1:17:23.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Look this way!  - That's real spiffy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.05,1:17:26.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice smile. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.31,1:17:31.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir. Can we get a statement?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.39,1:17:32.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like the picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.02,1:17:36.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Mr. Hoover!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.40,1:17:37.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.41,1:17:52.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go to the club?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.91,1:17:55.67,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After we drop Mother off at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.64,1:18:18.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have you at a table with Anita Colby.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.06,1:18:22.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Lela Rogers and her daughter Ginger  have asked if they can join.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.53,1:18:24.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's near the front.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.24,1:18:27.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rogers, pleasure to meet you.  This must be your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.45,1:18:28.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.62,1:18:31.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,J. Edgar Hoover. This is Clyde Tolson.  Anita, good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.21,1:18:42.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The bullet entered  the back of the head...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.30,1:18:44.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and exited through the front  near his cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.92,1:18:48.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that most people don't  realize is that there is little blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.47,1:18:52.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat from the bullet actually  seals the wound as it enters...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.30,1:18:57.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...so the crime scene is far more peaceful  than is depicted in your moving pictures.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.27,1:19:00.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And little Lindy.  Did you see the child with your own eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.48,1:19:03.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are details I wouldn't disclose...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.69,1:19:06.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a refined group of women  such as yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.53,1:19:12.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bear to make you shed a tear.  But I assure you this, we are on the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.58,1:19:15.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the Lindberghs in Paris.  I hardly recognized them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.83,1:19:16.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.00,1:19:20.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Only justice can bring reason  back to their lives.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.67,1:19:25.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But I might share one confidential  clue with you, if you swear to secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.72,1:19:27.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.01,1:19:30.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The gold notes from  the ransom money have surfaced.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.64,1:19:32.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And can you guess where?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.51,1:19:34.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us. Please, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.18,1:19:36.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In the Bronx, on three occasions.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.56,1:19:38.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And each one of the shop owners claim...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.60,1:19:42.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...they received them from a man with  a pointed chin and a German accent.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.36,1:19:48.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my word for it, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.36,1:19:51.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All the admiration in the world  can't fill the spot love goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.36,1:19:52.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.57,1:19:54.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Or keep your bed warm.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.70,1:19:58.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I serve my country, Miss Colby.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.75,1:20:01.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The nation's admiration  is more than enough for me. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.46,1:20:05.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But it likely makes for a cold bed.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.71,1:20:10.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, would it be out of the question  to bother you for a dance?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.34,1:20:12.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, how do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.47,1:20:15.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, simply a dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.60,1:20:17.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You do dance, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.47,1:20:20.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is a skill  that, um, I haven't yet mastered.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.19,1:20:24.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And the night is getting long,  isn't it, Mr. Tolson? Mr. Tolson?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.48,1:20:27.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No time like the present.  It's my favorite song, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.36,1:20:29.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time we leave.  Uh, we have a great deal of work.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.03,1:20:32.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We...  We have a great deal of work tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.41,1:20:36.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm afraid we don't have time  to dance. We're very busy, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.33,1:20:37.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.79,1:20:40.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And my sincere apologies. I...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.25,1:20:42.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Mr. Tolson.  Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.37,1:20:43.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Good evening.  - Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.00,1:20:45.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.30,1:20:50.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.26,1:20:52.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.47,1:20:55.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't... I don't like to...  I don't like to dance, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.43,1:20:58.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't like to da...  - Edgar, go look in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.56,1:21:01.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk the way the doctor taught you to.  Be my little Speedy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.78,1:21:14.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can spit my words out with... With...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.37,1:21:19.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can spit my words out with precision,  diction, and clarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.95,1:21:24.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can sp... Spit my words out with precision,  diction, and clarity.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.42,1:21:32.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a proficient, remarkable lad,  capable of remarkable feats.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.55,1:21:35.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a profic... Mother.  Mother, I don't like to dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.64,1:21:39.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mostly I don't like to dance with women.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.56,1:21:41.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's time you knew this.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.68,1:21:44.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I find it humiliating  and I refuse to be humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.48,1:21:46.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.98,1:21:49.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember Barton Pincus?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.19,1:21:52.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.94,1:21:54.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,His father was a watchmaker.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.66,1:21:58.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was 10 years younger than me  and you used to call him...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.79,1:22:03.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Birdy or Daffy  or something to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.00,1:22:06.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And do you remember  what happened to Daffy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.67,1:22:10.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After the school custodian discovered him  in a hoop skirt and flower bonnet?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.01,1:22:15.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was made to stand outside  in front of the school...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.68,1:22:18.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...wearing the bonnet and skirt  as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.55,1:22:22.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever wonder why  we called him Daffy?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.22,1:22:26.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For his odd behavior, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.06,1:22:30.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's short for "daffodil," Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.53,1:22:34.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what happened  to Daffodil Pincus?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.61,1:22:38.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother. He...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.20,1:22:41.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He shot himself six weeks after.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.24,1:22:42.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.20,1:22:47.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thank God every day that my own  sons don't suffer from his condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.21,1:22:49.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.42,1:22:54.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather have a dead son  than a daffodil for a son.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.39,1:23:02.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I'm gonna teach you to dance.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.77,1:23:08.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.97,1:23:45.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Bring this right over here, please.  - Sure, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.27,1:23:49.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Now, when did you get  this shipment?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.48,1:23:54.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long while back.  I'm thinking, uh, November 1931.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.82,1:23:57.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Three months before the kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.32,1:24:00.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.91,1:24:04.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The lumberyard is a cash business,  there aren't any receipts or names.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.53,1:24:07.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It tells us where he was shopping  before we were looking.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.58,1:24:10.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the addresses of where  the ransom bills have shown up.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.62,1:24:13.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 456 West Third.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.63,1:24:16.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And 476 West Third.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.30,1:24:18.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And down the street right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.30,1:24:24.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew who we were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.80,1:24:27.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who'd done business  in this neighborhood for years.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.14,1:24:29.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who was still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.60,1:24:31.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was average height, blue eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.90,1:24:33.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,High cheekbones and a pointy chin.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.98,1:24:38.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, a pointed chin  and an accent, like a...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.32,1:24:39.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,German accent, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.15,1:24:42.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A German with big cheekbones.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.66,1:24:46.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I, uh, going to get him  in some kind of trouble?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.45,1:24:50.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not if he didn't do anything wrong.  We're the FBl, son. We're the good guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.50,1:24:54.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was deposited by Walter Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.00,1:24:59.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He manages the gas station  up on Lexington and 127th.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.34,1:25:00.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Walter Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.42,1:25:03.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the man  that paid with this?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.30,1:25:05.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I remember him.  He bought 89 cents worth of gas.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.93,1:25:08.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And he paid with this bill?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.85,1:25:11.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. But I don't know him.  I haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.27,1:25:15.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You would remember him  if he came in again?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.19,1:25:18.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he was German, I think,  I mean, with an accent and pointed chin.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.69,1:25:21.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- High cheekbones, right?  - Yeah. I looked at the bill funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.53,1:25:24.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He assured me he had  a hundred more like it at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.20,1:25:25.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a conversation with him?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.49,1:25:27.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.58,1:25:29.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.79,1:25:32.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote down the license plate number.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.37,1:25:35.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the writing  along the edge of the bill.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.13,1:25:39.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.89,1:25:48.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, get Mr. Tolson.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.06,1:25:58.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Sisk.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.40,1:26:02.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The New York Motor Vehicles Bureau  describes it as a blue 1930 Dodge sedan.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.28,1:26:04.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The owner is a carpenter  born in Germany...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.40,1:26:08.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...lives at 1279 East 222nd Street  in the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.91,1:26:10.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Bruno Richard Hauptmann.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.13,1:26:23.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.38,1:26:25.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On September 19th, 1934...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.76,1:26:28.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...before we could arrest  the most wanted man in America...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.76,1:26:33.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he'd been pulled over by a local cop  for a broken tail light.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.18,1:26:34.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.85,1:26:38.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull over.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.61,1:26:47.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,FBl, put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.03,1:26:49.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Put them up!  - Ls there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.07,1:26:52.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the car!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.50,1:27:03.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bruno Hauptmann...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.71,1:27:07.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you are under arrest for the kidnapping  and murder of Charles Lindbergh, Jr.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.80,1:27:09.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuff him, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.31,1:27:17.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally had him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.48,1:27:20.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we had to convict,  but unlike trials of the past...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.81,1:27:26.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...we now had forensics,  expert witnesses, and facts.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.32,1:27:31.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We need a title, Agent Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.95,1:27:34.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.37,1:27:38.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We are working, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.33,1:27:39.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The tape came in.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.50,1:27:42.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it to my private office.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.84,1:27:45.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be all for now, Agent Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.27,1:28:05.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to say...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.15,1:28:09.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you looked so beautiful  sitting across that bar.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.74,1:28:11.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you watching me.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.70,1:28:13.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit I was watching you...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.74,1:28:15.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.62,1:28:20.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.12,1:28:22.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.42,1:28:26.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take this off.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.67,1:28:28.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.72,1:28:31.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.20,1:28:56.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, I told you  I am not to be disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.74,1:28:58.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Mr. Hoover?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.54,1:29:02.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's urgent. I have Agent Shanklin  on the line from Dallas.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.33,1:29:03.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.08,1:29:05.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Miss Gandy to put me through.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.79,1:29:08.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Agent Shanklin?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.55,1:29:11.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, the president has been shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.63,1:29:15.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.18,1:29:18.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No one, sir. I thought you should know  before the press reports it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.77,1:29:22.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you, Agent Shanklin.  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.53,1:29:31.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.05,1:30:00.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me Robert Kennedy immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.19,1:30:08.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.11,1:30:12.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kennedy,  the president has been shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.20,1:30:15.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.78,1:30:17.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover? What?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.49,1:30:21.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:34.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Frosty Mountain in front...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.05,1:30:36.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...by a length and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.30,1:30:38.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Jazz third by six.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.85,1:30:43.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Slapjack's fourth, final head.  Popstar Merell three quarters.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.56,1:30:48.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning for home, Frosty Mountain under  the left by a fraction and a length and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.52,1:30:51.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Number five. He's gaining on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.03,1:30:54.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Frosty Mountain, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.15,1:30:58.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I bet on that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.53,1:31:01.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah. We lost again, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.91,1:31:04.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dextro back by a half-length on the rail.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.50,1:31:07.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Dextro now making his move.  Findlay gives him the whip.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.75,1:31:09.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he goes, there he goes!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.67,1:31:11.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dextro, come on, Dextro!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.51,1:31:58.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Did you see his shoes?  - Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.13,1:32:00.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Desi Arnaz?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.38,1:32:03.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the crocodile ones  with the horrible buckles across the top?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.05,1:32:05.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't notice them one bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.77,1:32:08.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think with their money  they'd have a bit of fashion sense...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.60,1:32:10.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, ha.  - ...or at least pay someone to have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.02,1:32:12.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and his faux-ginger wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.77,1:32:17.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When she walked in, I thought a hunter  was gonna pull a rifle on that hat of hers.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.74,1:32:20.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like this, you see, like...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.74,1:32:22.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-ha-ha. That's right, with the feathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.54,1:32:29.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I care so very much  for you, Clyde. I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.83,1:32:34.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I love you, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.39,1:32:43.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,ls everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.89,1:32:45.14,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.80,1:32:47.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.48,1:32:53.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been meaning  to ask you something, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.98,1:32:54.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.32,1:33:01.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of Dorothy Lamour,  the actress?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.65,1:33:03.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,With Rudy Vallee at the Stork Club?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.45,1:33:05.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's the one.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.49,1:33:08.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a little camp for me, but, heh...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.71,1:33:14.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've been thinking of taking her up  on a proposal is all.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.17,1:33:17.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.80,1:33:19.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, not dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.67,1:33:22.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been to dinner several times now.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.01,1:33:25.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.93,1:33:29.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, in New York, when I've gone up  on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.52,1:33:33.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.06,1:33:40.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose what I'm... What I'm trying  to say here, Clyde, is, well...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.40,1:33:45.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l think it may be time for a Mrs. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.66,1:33:56.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't like her? Ls that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.71,1:33:59.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you make a fool of me, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.00,1:34:03.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not, Clyde,  I'm not making a fool of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.30,1:34:08.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you...? Have you become physical?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.81,1:34:12.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we have.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.06,1:34:14.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Clyde?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.48,1:34:19.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to be half a person?  Remain incomplete, is that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.52,1:34:22.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,ls that what I am to you, incompletion?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.28,1:34:25.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, pick that glass up immediately!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.24,1:34:27.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I will not! I have no reason to!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.99,1:34:30.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse! So, go on, fire me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.91,1:34:32.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it. Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.37,1:34:34.91,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself.  You're acting like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.08,1:34:36.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Agh!  - Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.08,1:34:39.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde! You have no shoes on,  for God's sakes!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.75,1:34:42.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, I will not!  I won't even listen to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.59,1:34:45.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never tell me what to do!  You just lost that right!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.59,1:34:47.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop it!  - I see right through you!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.51,1:34:50.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a scared, heartless,  horrible little man!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.93,1:34:52.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Unh! Don't you dare!  - Unh!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.51,1:35:32.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you ever do that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.14,1:35:35.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.64,1:35:39.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Cly...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.98,1:35:42.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.11,1:35:46.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, please. Clyde, don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.74,1:35:47.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.07,1:35:49.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.99,1:35:51.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, please don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.99,1:35:53.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.33,1:35:57.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Clyde! Clyde, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.00,1:36:00.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.75,1:36:09.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we have another day of races.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.10,1:36:20.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever mention a lady friend again...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.77,1:36:23.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...it will be the last time  that you share my company.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.95,1:36:37.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Love you, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.66,1:36:40.83,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.21,1:36:47.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Meter looks promising.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.56,1:37:04.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Unh. Ugh.  - What is it, Clyde?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.06,1:37:06.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.77,1:37:08.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.32,1:37:09.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.65,1:37:13.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get a doctor now!  Someone get a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.74,1:37:16.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Clyde, look at me. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.83,1:37:19.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone get a doctor now!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.58,1:37:21.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.25,1:37:23.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll recover most of his function...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.25,1:37:26.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but a stroke like this,  it will limit the hours he can work...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.42,1:37:28.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the information he can process.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.17,1:37:29.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Mr. Hoover?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.59,1:37:34.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm fine. I just... I was playing  with my dog in the yard on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.26,1:37:36.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it's dehydration.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.10,1:37:40.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That could do it, but it may be wise  to reduce your hours as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.39,1:37:42.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,At your age, it's important to take leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.48,1:37:46.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, please, give us some privacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.78,1:37:55.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you, if you ever denigrate me  in front of my staff again...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.36,1:37:58.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll have you railroaded out of your  profession. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.45,1:38:00.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.45,1:38:02.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.29,1:38:05.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have for energy?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.29,1:38:08.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We have diet medications  which tend to give a boost.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.79,1:38:12.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So I could lose a few pounds  and have more energy as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.46,1:38:15.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't worry about your weight, sir.  It's solid weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.51,1:38:16.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.47,1:38:18.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Schedule a daily visit.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.51,1:38:21.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.48,1:38:34.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They're giving King the Nobel Prize.  Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.32,1:38:37.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The degenerates and radicals  are being lifted up internationally.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.49,1:38:40.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it's 1920 all over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.99,1:38:42.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.00,1:38:45.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When he finds out  that we have this audiotape...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.79,1:38:48.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that we know the truth  about his character...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.17,1:38:51.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's going to decline the award,  Clyde, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.96,1:38:54.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President Johnson...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.21,1:38:55.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.84,1:38:57.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Clyde.  - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.18,1:39:01.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna have to learn to enunciate.  I can't seem to understand you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.26,1:39:05.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no legal tools.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.43,1:39:08.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, our laws have not kept pace...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.19,1:39:10.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with the improved tactics  of today's criminals.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.02,1:39:12.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do this for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.07,1:39:15.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your idea?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.53,1:39:18.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we have friends in the press, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.36,1:39:21.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We plant stories with them to ensure...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.45,1:39:25.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the activities of suspected radicals  see the light of day.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.00,1:39:27.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll trace it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.50,1:39:30.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, only if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.00,1:39:33.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's called counterintelligence,  Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.17,1:39:36.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The more untrue the story,  the more dramatic the impact.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.67,1:39:39.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'm going to send  the hotel recording...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.84,1:39:44.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...along with a personal letter  the day before he gets the Nobel Prize.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.39,1:39:48.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if he accepts the award,  we'll send the tape straight to the press.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.02,1:39:54.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you want to be involved  with that kind of surveillance?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.07,1:39:57.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's why the letter  won't be from me.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.78,1:40:00.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a fictitious letter  from one of his own.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.74,1:40:07.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there can be no room for error.  I'm not sure that we could ensu...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.50,1:40:11.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot understand what  you're saying, Clyde. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.25,1:40:14.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now. Learn to speak up.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.22,1:40:22.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen, I'm gonna need you  in the office tomorrow. No time to relent.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.22,1:40:26.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.73,1:40:29.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.81,1:40:31.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.60,1:40:36.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd think after all this time  she'd be able to cook my egg correctly.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.11,1:40:40.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are in these shots?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.45,1:40:41.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just vitamins...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.86,1:40:43.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...a little extra pick-me-up.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.34,1:40:57.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Look into your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.92,1:41:02.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you are a complete fraud  and a great liability to all of us Negroes."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.93,1:41:06.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "us," Miss Gandy, "us," not "the."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.80,1:41:08.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a Negro now, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.43,1:41:11.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Write every word as I say it,  is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.48,1:41:14.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, "White people in this country  have enough frauds of their own...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.15,1:41:17.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they do not  have one at this time...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.32,1:41:19.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that is anywhere near your equal.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.40,1:41:22.32,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- I repeat..."  - Sir, what is this exercise?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.49,1:41:26.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy, I am not going to entertain  questions during my dictation, now write.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.79,1:41:32.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"I repeat, you are a colossal fraud  and an evil, vicious one, at that!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.92,1:41:36.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not believe in God. You do not  believe in any personal moral principles!"
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.92,1:41:39.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, may I ask who this  will be addressed to...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.38,1:41:41.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The question is not to whom,  Miss Gandy, not to whom...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.09,1:41:45.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but from whom and it is not from  this office, is that understood?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.51,1:41:47.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"You have turned out to be not a leader...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.93,1:41:51.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but a dissolute, abnormal,  moral imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.60,1:41:54.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing left to do  and you know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.52,1:41:57.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's but one way out,  and you better take it...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.19,1:42:02.28,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...before your filthy, abnormal,  fraudulent self is bared to this nation."
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.44,1:42:04.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.91,1:42:07.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Edgar.  - Type it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.24,1:42:09.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Type it up.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.21,1:42:18.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you work for our  PR department, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.04,1:42:20.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For two years now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.92,1:42:24.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you are familiar  with my earlier work...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.26,1:42:27.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...against Edward Clarke  and his Ku Klux Klan, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.89,1:42:29.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.22,1:42:32.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was arrested for a violation  of the white slave traffic act...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.39,1:42:35.77,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for crossing state lines  to have an affair with a white woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.94,1:42:36.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ls that correct, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.15,1:42:41.23,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct. It was the strongest law  at my disposal at the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.40,1:42:45.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know  that I'm very proud of that work.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.57,1:42:48.95,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Gandy told me that you stopped  with Bruno Hauptmann's arrest.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.12,1:42:52.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Would you like to start there?  - Yes, yes, I think we shall.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.42,1:42:58.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hauptmann was brought to trial...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.38,1:43:00.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...on January 2nd, 1935.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.92,1:43:06.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,H.L. Mencken called this  the biggest story since the resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.43,1:43:10.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of things,  this may be bigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.22,1:43:12.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, no two saws  make the same markings.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.81,1:43:16.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This saw from Bruno Hauptmann's  tool chest makes markings identical...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.60,1:43:19.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to those found on the ladder  used in the crime.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.56,1:43:21.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ransom note  and Mr. Hauptmann's writings...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.15,1:43:27.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he wrote the word "anyding"  for "anything", uh, "gut" for "good"...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.03,1:43:32.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,..."boad" for "boat,"  and notice the inverted capital N's.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.70,1:43:35.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Y's that look like J's.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.87,1:43:37.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Lindbergh, you said you heard a voice...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.12,1:43:39.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the cemetery that night.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.63,1:43:41.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.04,1:43:44.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice,  to the best of my belief...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.80,1:43:48.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...calling Dr. Condon in a foreign accent.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.63,1:43:49.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, doctor."
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.80,1:43:50.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Since that time...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.01,1:43:52.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...have you heard the same voice?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.97,1:43:54.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.64,1:43:57.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose voice was it  that you heard in the cemetery that night...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.81,1:43:59.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...saying, "Hey, doctor"?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.81,1:44:01.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Hauptmann's voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.15,1:44:05.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But did he act alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.28,1:44:11.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He never confessed,  but what sociopath ever does?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.37,1:44:13.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The evidence was clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.28,1:44:18.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He was indicted for murder in the  first degree while perpetrating a burglary.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.71,1:44:22.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In New Jersey,  that is punishable by death.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.17,1:44:23.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hauptmann...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.54,1:44:26.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've had an opportunity  in this courtroom today...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.17,1:44:28.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to tell the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.38,1:44:29.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.97,1:44:32.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I told the truth already.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.34,1:44:33.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And the statements...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.60,1:44:36.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to District Attorney Foley.  Did you tell him the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.97,1:44:38.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To a certain extent.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.43,1:44:42.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,To a certain extent you didn't  tell him the truth. Ls that right?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.19,1:44:49.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This board that was found  in your closet, S-204...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.11,1:44:52.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...has these numbers written on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.03,1:44:54.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little blurred now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.03,1:44:56.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.49,1:44:59.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Between are some words.  It looks like Decatur and Sedgwick.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.45,1:45:00.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You see that?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.29,1:45:05.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what that means, don't you?  That address on there?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.04,1:45:07.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.59,1:45:11.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the address and telephone number  of Dr. Condon...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.72,1:45:13.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the man who paid the ransom...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.38,1:45:17.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...written in your writing,  found on a board in your closet.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.47,1:45:20.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover, the doctor's here to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.85,1:45:22.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Following Dr. King's historic speech...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.15,1:45:26.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...many said that day brought about a new  awakening in the conscience of the nation.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.15,1:45:29.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Others called it a national disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.74,1:45:34.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,In the long history of man's cruelty to man,  this was a day of hope.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.57,1:45:35.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dream...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.99,1:45:39.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that one day...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.62,1:45:43.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...this nation will rise up...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.50,1:45:46.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live out the true meaning  of its creeds.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.09,1:45:51.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A man's legacy is determined by where  the story ends, Agent Owens.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.80,1:45:54.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's think about that tonight  and make a decision tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.47,1:45:56.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ls this about a man's legacy?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.43,1:46:00.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Or an institution's reputation?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.43,1:46:03.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The two are connected, Agent Owens.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.44,1:46:05.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One invented the other and vice versa.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.10,1:46:07.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.40,1:46:10.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.11,1:46:14.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We the jury find the defendant,  Bruno Richard Hauptmann...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.65,1:46:16.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...guilty of murder in the first degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.79,1:46:30.71,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Honor,  I ask for immediate sentencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.80,1:46:37.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the law of this state...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.59,1:46:40.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...l rule that Mr. Bruno Hauptmann  suffer death...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.06,1:46:46.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...at the time and place  and in the manner provided by law.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.82,1:46:56.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's death for Hauptmann!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.16,1:47:03.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The trial of the century...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.66,1:47:08.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...the criminal shamed,  the FBl cemented as the public hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.63,1:47:11.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our, that's our ending, agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.51,1:47:15.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But did he do it alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.55,1:47:18.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the one who actually took the child?  How can you be sure?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.72,1:47:23.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the mountain of evidence  we discovered, uncovered...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.81,1:47:26.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...confirmed, and clarified,  you cannot dispute it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.85,1:47:29.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Clarence Darrow did.  - Of course. Heh.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.19,1:47:32.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Agent Owens.  That's what he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.36,1:47:34.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Roosevelt issued  a statement questioning his guilt.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.07,1:47:40.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she has enough to hide on her own  when it comes to un-American activities.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.74,1:47:46.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're comfortable with it  as an ending, I'll do my best with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.12,1:47:50.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.83,1:47:52.33,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.92,1:47:58.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.22,1:48:01.05,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He received my letter  and the audio tape last night.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.22,1:48:03.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,President Johnson affixes his signature...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.39,1:48:04.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...using more than 100 pens.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.64,1:48:07.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the coveted souvenirs  goes to the Nobel prize-winner...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.77,1:48:10.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Martin Luther King,  a dedicated leader...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.19,1:48:12.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, say it, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.36,1:48:17.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It just seems so risky, Edgar,  over a couple negative articles.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.53,1:48:21.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's deliberately surrounded himself  with communists...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.24,1:48:25.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and, with the power he's gathering,  he's now our greatest domestic threat.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.20,1:48:30.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,On behalf of the Nobel Committee...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.75,1:48:34.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...we hand over to you the insignia...  - He's going to decline the award, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.75,1:48:37.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows what we have can ruin him.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.42,1:48:42.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- -Of the Nobel Peace Prize,  the diploma and the gold medal.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.31,1:48:49.06,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no question about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.89,1:48:51.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's done.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.07,1:48:58.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept the Nobel Prize for Peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.28,1:49:06.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...at a moment when 22 million Negroes  of the United States...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.62,1:49:09.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...are enga...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.97,1:49:31.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sorry to interrupt, sir.  - Your next appointment is here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.14,1:49:34.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor first, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.65,1:49:36.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.32,1:49:42.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Send him in in a few minutes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.94,1:51:44.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.31,1:52:17.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay strong, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.60,1:52:20.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong. Unh!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.42,1:52:47.30,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The parade as it makes its way...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.46,1:52:49.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Capitol Building  for the inauguration.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.51,1:52:56.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the Roosevelt High  Marching Band leading the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.27,1:53:03.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The motorcade is making progress  down Pennsylvania Avenue...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.06,1:53:08.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...carrying our 37th president.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.20,1:53:16.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Richard Milhous Nixon  waves to the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.04,1:53:20.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, there's the president  and his wife Pat...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.58,1:53:22.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...happily waving.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.08,1:54:00.41,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,When morals decline...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.20,1:54:03.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and good men do nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.54,1:54:06.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...evil flourishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.92,1:54:14.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Every citizen has a duty to learn of this  that threatens his home...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.09,1:54:17.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...his children.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.60,1:54:25.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,A society uninterested and unwilling  to learn from the past...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.73,1:54:27.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.99,1:54:33.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We must never forget our history.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.74,1:54:42.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We must never lower our guard.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.17,1:54:55.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Even today, there are organizations  that have America as their prime target.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.43,1:54:59.68,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,They would destroy the safety  and the happiness of every individual...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.89,1:55:03.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and thrust us into  a condition of lawlessness...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.47,1:55:07.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...immorality that passes the imagination.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.98,1:55:11.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The president will see you now,  Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.98,1:55:13.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.62,1:55:26.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.47,1:55:40.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I am so sorry, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.51,1:55:42.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't answering your telephone.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.77,1:55:46.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a photo session  with a retiring agent.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.60,1:55:48.02,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.02,1:55:50.35,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Clyde?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.86,1:55:56.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bad day for him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.03,1:56:03.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you...? Will you schedule  a dinner for us, please...
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.04,1:56:06.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...in our old corner booth?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.37,1:56:09.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid he's too tired today, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.04,1:56:12.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you'd like to dine at his house?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.38,1:56:14.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.13,1:56:17.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.22,1:56:20.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.77,1:56:27.81,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Helen?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.06,1:56:33.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.07,1:56:38.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I kill everything that I love?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.07,1:56:44.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not gone yet, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.58,1:56:50.62,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything that we've built?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.58,1:56:52.58,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.17,1:56:56.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bureau is stronger  than just you and me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.21,1:57:01.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your child is sure  and keeps this country safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.47,1:57:09.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Helen, if any...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.35,1:57:14.86,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,if anything ever happens to me, I need you  to do something for me, do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.48,1:57:17.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.61,1:57:22.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Nixon, he's gonna come for it all.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.20,1:57:26.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll crucify me and my Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.49,1:57:34.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of what will happen  if I'm not here to protect it, Miss Gandy.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.63,1:57:36.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Your private files, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.09,1:57:42.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then no one will ever find them.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.30,1:57:46.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.65,1:58:00.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of pressure  they put on?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.36,1:58:03.20,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.36,1:58:04.99,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.99,1:58:08.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much pressure.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.50,1:58:12.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.17,1:58:15.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Helen.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.76,1:58:31.10,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, did Nixon ask for your resignation?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.27,1:58:35.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he wanted to know  what we had in the files on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.35,1:58:37.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.52,1:58:41.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "What files, sir?"
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.53,1:58:43.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But he knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.86,1:58:48.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants us to expand our wiretaps  to include news reporters now, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.95,1:58:53.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that, especially not now.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.45,1:58:55.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the problem, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.33,1:59:00.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't agree to do his black bag jobs,  he'll create his own private force.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.67,1:59:03.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's illegal.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.55,1:59:09.22,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, he didn't say it outright,  but I saw it in his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.39,1:59:11.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't be controlled, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.56,1:59:15.48,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a menace who'll do anything  to hold on to power.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.73,1:59:18.73,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.56,1:59:23.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. See, I never played his game,  that's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.07,1:59:26.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if to some what I did  seemed like rule-bending...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.70,1:59:30.12,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...then perhaps they need to figure out  what it is they did...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.28,1:59:33.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that made them feel blackmailed  or intimidated.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.25,1:59:36.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.50,1:59:41.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what? What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.59,1:59:46.38,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it might be time  for us to retire.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.43,1:59:48.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.72,1:59:53.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You built a great thing, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.35,1:59:57.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you stop now,  you'll be celebrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.52,2:00:00.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you've  always wanted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.77,2:00:03.44,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Our country's lasting adoration?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.61,2:00:06.11,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's a chance you could have it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.94,2:00:10.36,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes, and why wouldn't I? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.53,2:00:12.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't I, Clyde?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.33,2:00:15.87,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved this country  from a Bolshevik invasion...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.04,2:00:19.96,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...rid this country of radicals,  captured Machine Gun Kelly...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.12,2:00:23.54,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed Dillinger, captured Karpis,  convicted Bruno Hauptmann.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.75,2:00:27.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, with my last breath  when I try to help save this country again...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.51,2:00:30.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm rewarded with a forced retirement?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.18,2:00:32.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not go down,  and the fact that you suggest that...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.14,2:00:35.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...makes me question your very loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.56,2:00:38.56,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,My loyalty, Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.77,2:00:41.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your loyalty, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.27,2:00:45.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I read your manuscript, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.15,2:00:48.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't arrest Karpis.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.65,2:00:52.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know as well as I do  there was no white horse in the street...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.82,2:00:56.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...no gun in the back seat.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.99,2:01:01.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you didn't kill Dillinger.  Agent Purvis did.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.00,2:01:05.88,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,But you kept all the glory for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.21,2:01:10.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And Machine Gun Kelly never said,  "Don't shoot, G-Men."
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.51,2:01:16.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You made that up  to sell comic books, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.52,2:01:22.31,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And when we went to the scene  of the greatest crime of the century...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.90,2:01:26.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mr. Lindbergh didn't come out  and shake your hand...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.11,2:01:31.57,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and express his faith in the FBl.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.74,2:01:38.03,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He called you a fussy little man,  and he refused to even meet you.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.37,2:01:43.00,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you didn't arrest Hauptmann.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.17,2:01:46.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Agent Sisk did.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.63,2:01:51.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't even at the scene, Edgar.  Only the photo op.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.30,2:01:55.34,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, most of what you wrote  is exaggeration...
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.51,2:02:00.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...some of it blatant lies, and I don't  even know if you realize it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.77,2:02:04.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.06,2:02:09.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can lie to everyone else,  the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.23,2:02:12.90,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for your own sake,  for the sake of the Bureau...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.61,2:02:15.74,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you cannot lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.24,2:02:22.66,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've never given you  your job, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.42,2:02:25.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.92,2:02:30.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't even qualified.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.30,2:02:36.26,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember the day  you came in for your interview?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.47,2:02:39.18,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.27,2:02:45.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You walked into my office  and you fixed my window...
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.81,2:02:48.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...you picked up my handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.94,2:02:50.61,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You handed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.99,2:02:55.65,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember why I was sweating,  Clyde?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.20,2:02:59.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you were exercising.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.95,2:03:03.29,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.50,2:03:06.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sweating because I...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.29,2:03:09.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew at that very moment...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.30,2:03:13.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew at that very moment that I...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.13,2:03:16.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I needed you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.30,2:03:21.97,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've never needed anyone else  in my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.06,2:03:25.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.52,2:03:29.94,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,So I began to perspire.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.86,2:03:32.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.99,2:03:37.49,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Edgar, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.49,2:03:39.82,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, it's...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.95,2:03:45.16,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just indigestion, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.75,2:03:52.92,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to dinner tomorrow night,  shall we? Our old corner booth.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.59,2:03:56.17,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps if I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.34,2:03:58.09,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.26,2:03:59.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And you must...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.68,2:04:04.47,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,You must...  We have a great many things to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.64,2:04:08.52,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I can't trust anyone else  at the Bureau right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.02,2:04:11.98,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Can only depend on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.50,2:04:33.50,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.43,2:04:49.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Clyde.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.52,2:04:53.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Edgar.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.05,2:05:20.59,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Mr. Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.76,2:05:21.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.97,2:05:24.64,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Bozo, Bozo, G-Boy, come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.80,2:05:27.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The very essence of our democracy...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.18,2:05:32.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...is rooted in a belief  in the worth of the individual.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.27,2:05:38.15,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That life has meaning that transcends  any man-made system...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.78,2:05:42.45,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that love is the greatest force  on earth...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.11,2:05:46.78,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...far more enduring than hatred...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.83,2:05:51.79,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...or the unnatural divisions of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.47,2:06:03.63,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.34,2:06:07.80,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Annie from Mr. Hoover's residence.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.97,2:06:10.39,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoover has passed.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.34,2:06:40.55,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yeah?  - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.17,2:06:46.51,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.18,2:06:49.43,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,That old cocksucker.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.60,2:06:52.27,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a speech prepared.  We should go on television.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.43,2:06:53.93,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.10,2:06:58.40,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,First seal off his office, change his locks,  do whatever you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.56,2:07:01.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I want those fucking files.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.03,2:07:03.19,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.04,2:07:13.70,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.54,2:07:16.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.92,2:07:24.21,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,He's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.51,2:09:32.84,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen, it is with  a profound sense of personal loss...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.01,2:09:36.01,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I learned of the death  of J. Edgar Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.68,2:09:40.85,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,This truly remarkable man  has served his country for 48 years...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.02,2:09:43.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...under eight presidents,  as director of the FBl...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.85,2:09:49.69,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...with unparalleled devotion  and ability and dedication.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.86,2:09:54.53,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,For 25 years, from the time I came to  Washington as a freshman congressman...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.07,2:09:59.37,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...he has been one of my closest  personal friends and advisors.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.54,2:10:03.46,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,And every American, in my opinion,  owes J. Edgar Hoover a great debt...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.62,2:10:08.04,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...for building the FBl into the finest  law enforcement organization...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.21,2:10:10.13,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.96,2:10:16.89,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,I've ordered that all the flags of the  government buildings be flown at half mast...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.05,2:10:19.72,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I will say that, in doing so,  that Edgar Hoover...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.89,2:10:24.60,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...because of his indomitable courage  against sometimes very vicious attack...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.77,2:10:31.07,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...has made certain that the flag of the FBl  will always fly high.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.24,2:10:38.24,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,The FBl is the eternal monument  honoring this great American.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.24,2:10:42.08,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny how even the dearest face...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.25,2:10:44.75,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...will fade away in time...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.29,2:10:50.25,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...but most clearly I remember your eyes  with a sort of teasing smile in them...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.67,2:10:53.42,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the feeling of that soft spot...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.59,2:10:56.76,Default_英文,,0000,0000,0000,,...just northeast  of the corner of your mouth.

Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,片名：胡佛  翻譯：米粒@豆瓣 weibo@conanemily  交流分享 請勿商用 保護版權 人人有責
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[胡佛]這麼跟你說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南方基督教領袖會議和共產主義有直接聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最偉大的人也有腐壞的可能  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共產主義並不是政治黨派的一種  這是瘟疫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它會腐蝕靈魂  把最紳士的人們...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...變成惡毒、邪惡的暴君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們所見到的全是  對法律和指令的不屑一顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪率激增
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廣泛、公然地蔑視我們的權威...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...記住我這句話  倘若此事不被及時遏制
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它會把我們國家再次  拉向無政府狀態的深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.47,0:01:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切的開始總是平靜的  不是嗎，埃爾文先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須接受這個事實...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...那就是你本可以幫著避免  爆炸案和暴力事件的發生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更感興趣的是  它是如何描述您和您掌管的聯邦調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我辛苦工作了這麼長時間  真的不能就這樣退居幕後...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...來眼睜睜地看著壞人再次吸引  大家的眼球 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於臭名昭著這件事  有件有趣的事實...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...尤其是當它的來源是崇拜  或是名望...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...如果不加以控制  將不可避免地變成壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議您好好看看  這次爭辯的真正目的...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...在徹底毀掉您最心愛的事情的名聲之前  我們都知道那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[對講機響]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[海倫]來自《犯罪紀實》的作者到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...公關辦公室找來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他安排在我外面的辦公室  帶上打字機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪小姐 是時候讓這代人  知道我這版本的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- [海倫]馬上就好  - 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是1919年，史密斯調查員...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在司法部的第一任上司...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是總檢察長A·米切爾·帕爾默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是貴格會信仰者  （貴格會，基督教信教的一個派別）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不信奉戰爭  但他理解力量和決斷的必要性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們從史學家那裡瞭解到的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...通常都是從現在的角度來看  疏忽了前後關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米切爾·帕爾默是個英雄人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你沒事吧？  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒事吧？  - 我想是的，是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒事了 沒事了  - 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎？已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 帕爾默和激進者的鬥爭  正和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的 他也是目標  他並不是唯一一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一晚全國各地一共  有8枚炸彈爆炸 全都是在晚上11點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位國家參議員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四位內閣成員  一位最高法院法官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約翰·D·洛克菲勒，J·P·摩根...  （洛克菲勒，美國實業家，標準石油創辦人；摩根，美國銀行家）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們都成了  布爾什維克共產主義分子的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 整棟樓都晃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言 激進者的炸彈襲擊事件  過去得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只在路中間留下了他的血跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是檢察人員用桶子來收拾殘局  而不是收集證據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們丟掉了他的槍  而不是保存指紋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你也看得到  這不算什麼愚蠢的警察的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個時候  這是正常的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家或許就要完了 德懷特
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是1919年  還沒人正視過犯罪科學...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有聯邦權利機構  沒有聯邦調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那晚我的眼界被打開了  就是那一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你的鄰居嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他在我辦公室工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「會有一次謀殺行動  我們殺戮因為它必須存在」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我們以毀滅來擺脫  你們這個獨裁主義的國家」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那晚在帕爾默檢察長的家裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們把這一點  留給讀者想像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我們賦予主角一些神秘感  還是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以暗示是一個  您提到過的年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對兩邊都好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的法學文憑是哪裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬治華盛頓大學  我是本地人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要照顧家母  所以不敢遠遊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在這學校還取得了英語專業文憑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不需要我來告訴你  決定一個人的遺產的關鍵...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常都是眼睛所不能看見的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的重點是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要重申  惡棍和英雄的區別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這區別  和今天的標準相比呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不確定  我想要知道更多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以明天再來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 但這些寫好的得留下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再會 史密斯調查員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太大聲說話總是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.78,0:06:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕爾默先生讓你參與今天的緊急會議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格萊德維爾小姐 請記住...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩點鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次別去太早  跟遲到一樣無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位秘書處新來的美麗女士又是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海倫 自我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你 胡佛先生  我叫海倫·甘迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也很高興見到你  歡迎來司法部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以告知帕爾默先生我會出席
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他總是這麼迷人  我做事不會太認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑瑞米 我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要...幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪西亞夫人今早給我算了一卦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她預感說  我應該買條裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說你的父親不久就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死後  你會成為這個國家最有權勢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥是個好人  埃德加...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你會讓我們家族復興
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加？我煩到你了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在聽著呢 媽媽  你解雇了女傭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴她幹完活  就可以自己走人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再為她的肆無忌憚付工錢  整個黑人階級都要公開造反了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我可以開展調查  - 日子過得太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽見我剛才說的了嗎？  我說 我可以開展調查了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直說吧什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕爾默先生今天叫我參與了一個會議  和布爾什維克的戰爭已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他堅持讓我領導  一個新的反激進分子的部門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是像條小狗一樣歡呼雀躍了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴他  這是我們國家面臨過的最大威脅...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在感覺到自己會有所成效之前  是不會接受這份工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮 但你還是會接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年薪有三千呢 媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得給你買點新衣服  你不能再穿成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅4小時之後  我就掌握了40個激進分子的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月底之前應該會有一萬個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有自己的員工  可以信任的調查員們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 你在抽煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不會自覺去抽的 媽  - 聽醫生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有它分散一下  你的勇氣會更迸發出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會想落得跟你爸一樣的下場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就去抽根煙  把你爸扶到房間去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得準備一下去吃晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚你要拋下我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和一位打字員  她很有條理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.82,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會給她展示我在國會圖書館的  卡片編目系統
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給她製造點浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴藍色的領帶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你戴藍色領帶特別帥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還從沒來過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我幫忙整編好了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 每件物品都有它  自己的索引卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著自己特有的編碼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,標明了標題 作者 位置 主題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去需要好幾天時間來找的東西  現在只需要幾分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 說個作者或者題目 隨便什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「不檢點行為」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼年代？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 幫我計時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.16,0:11:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道我不是在說  「政治不檢點」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜歡呢  我可以重找一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我花了多長時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一分鐘 零10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下 如果這個國家的每個公民  都可以如此唯一可識別...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過他們自己的卡片和編號  比如說 指紋圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想看 如果他們犯了罪  我們可以多麼迅速地抓到他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都太棒了 約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要繼續呆在這裡  還是想去別的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.88,0:12:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定你想讓事情如何發展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我們倆只是認識了很短的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我肯定你會是最好的伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量 人格  還有教育
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在取笑我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不 不 當然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那胡佛先生 請站起來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會非常感激  假如你不會把這些...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴任何你的打字員同事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  能否問問...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我的人格有什麼缺陷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們才剛認識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我相信我在判斷人格方面  又快又準
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經約會三次  但我已不需要更多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多數人還需要 但我不用  我能一眼看穿別人是怎樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 請叫我埃德加  我母親就是這樣叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 埃德加？  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能保守一個秘密嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 說到做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對結婚沒有興趣  工作才是第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那或許你可以考慮  做我的私人秘書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正如那個圖書館一樣  規整了調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人說其實二者都不需要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 創新者總是不受待見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是一開始不受待見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪家那個蠢孩子  又呼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他需要換尿布了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是該看看總檢察長  需要些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我需要洛杉磯那邊錄音的  完全副本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到了那些以後  才會回復他的呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 史密斯調查員回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對於帕爾默襲擊案還有些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他走？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海倫 你喜歡他嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對他還沒有什麼看法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡他  我信任他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那我把他安排到你外面的辦公室  - 不 不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬個桌子讓他到裡面來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在1920年  我該如何保護我們機構不受任何人影響？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搬來這個辦公室之前  我們毫無權力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們受制幾條聯邦法律  無權攜帶軍火...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國會也喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪者被釋放  但也沒有法律禁制我們追蹤他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我自己做了個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我彙編了超過5000個名字的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後聯繫了華盛頓的一個部門...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們仍有一小部分  未經檢驗的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是勞工部嗎？  是不是他們有驅逐出境的權利？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們只驅逐  滿足以下兩個條件的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須是外國人  必須是他們的工作會損害我們國家的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們和您合作了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.35,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在華盛頓 沒人會就這樣跟你  分享他們的權力 史密斯調查員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是沒有可依據的法律  來授權...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來逮捕一個外國人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我已經證明了他可以被驅逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何證據的情況下  不行 檢察官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 應該遵循正當法律程序  - 正當法律程序？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他們對我們國家有威脅啊？  - 或許是有...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 確實對我們國家有威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有犯罪的證據  我們就沒有理由將其驅逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會聯繫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們的領導之一是  卡密內蒂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他厭煩了我們的司法部  但他更加討厭的是另一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個天生的革命家...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要呼籲反對和抵抗  侵略的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用一切手段 包括暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾瑪·古德曼  她是激進運動的英雄人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們可以把她交給卡密內蒂  他會毫不猶豫地將她驅逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她是美國公民
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您需要休息一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道今天的你想像這些很難  但曾經...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通的美國公民會擔心  他們的安全和生活 史密斯調查員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在芝加哥 由共產主義勞工發起的  煤礦罷工造成了大面積停電
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著就是騷亂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後在停戰紀念日那天  華盛頓州的森特勒利亞...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛從戰場載譽歸來的老兵  被激進主義分子暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紅色革命的火焰  已經蔓延到了我們國家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們不能逐個擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣他們會轉移到地下  那每個參議員的信箱裡都會有炸彈的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要同一時間的突襲  把他們一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 「他們」又是誰？  - 你就是來解決這個問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我需要我們國家每個激進分子  都有一張卡片來代表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠牆放 先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道他們是誰 從哪裡來  隸屬什麼組織 有什麼計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些已經有犯罪記錄的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更關心的是他們是否有犯罪的打算  請靠牆放 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們有多少人？  - 現在只有你們四個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會把鎖安上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 甘迪小姐  那會吸引過多的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何東西都不許按字母順序排列
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要這些卡片以主題和類型分類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個系統應該簡潔明瞭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是  找到特定的信息就變得沒有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要相信任何人  甚至我們的同事探員
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡半數的工作人員  還另有兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們調查的犯罪並不是犯罪  只是犯罪的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的這個想法...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠牆放 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如你的想法是來我們國家  圖謀推翻政權...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼當然 這就是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古德曼女士嫁給了一位美國公民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她嫁給的這個男人從未探監過她  但是這個男人...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從婚禮以來就一直和此人同居的  他每晚都拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如你突襲了這群人  但毫無斬獲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有槍支 沒有炸彈  只是驅逐了無辜的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家的每個角落  都有美國公民...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敦促總檢察長有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還美國一份和平
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我很樂意向帕爾默先生  傳達你的異議
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但同時  要揭發古德曼小姐令人不齒的婚姻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還得把你的衣服給換了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你說什麼 約翰？  - 你的西服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要尊重自己  更重要的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尊重我們部門
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.71,0:20:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古德曼小姐  你是否是無政府主義者？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你否認自己是無政府主義者？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否堅信應該推翻  美國政府的統治？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否主張  暗殺公共官員？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕回答
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位外國公民拒絕回答任何  這份法庭令中要求的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們已經給了她一切機會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的提議是驅逐出境
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 我們有了一個先例
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 我現在安排一下  情人節我們去帕特森的出行？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 甘迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2月14日 我乘坐火車  去了新澤西州的帕特森
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能抓住這些激進分子  哪怕他們只是犯了輕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勞工部就必須把他們送上  回家的客船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以調查局的探員們  還有當地警力...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始在已知有共產主義激進分子的地方  集聚起來準備突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全國上下都是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人持械 行為暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人為了拘捕可以大開殺戒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿一支 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們允許用這個嗎？  - 這些算是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有法律可以阻止我們使用自己的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們 拿好自己的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察！這是突擊檢查！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要從窗子逃走了  快阻止！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.32,0:22:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳單內容完全吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們破了爆炸案
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終 我們逮捕了將近  4000名共產主義激進分子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐出境了500多人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成得很靠運氣  也冒著巨大的個人風險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們發現了假冒的記者  五支手槍 兩支自動槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在特雷敦 他們找到了火藥  銅 銅絲 還有電池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一個軍工廠  - 是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底特律逮捕了120人  費城有41人 這裡目前有17人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但調查局裡和此事有關的人  都丟了飯碗 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至帕爾默他自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些確實 但也算是教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以看到 爆炸案停止了  恢復了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.81,0:24:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國人民逐漸忘記了  曾經有如此一種威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以當政治對手們  攻擊帕爾默的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲稱保護國家不受共產主義侵蝕...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.86,0:24:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的同胞們就這樣熟視無睹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為就像今天 他們已經忘記了  那些炸彈 那些流血犧牲 那些恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼是帕爾默而不是你  因為其實是你安排了那些突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時只有24歲  只是服從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.50,0:24:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有這次行動  你很有可能就出生在一個共產主義的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.51,0:24:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是你今天如此熱愛的祖國
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.39,0:24:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我說的對嗎？  - 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.47,0:24:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.68,0:24:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別管他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.85,0:24:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在開會 托爾森  馬上就出去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.07,0:24:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記跟檢察官的會面 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.57,0:24:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文件還沒準備好 托爾森  你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.91,0:25:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您 抱歉  我今晚就會寫好這一章
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.04,0:25:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 史密斯調查員
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.10,0:25:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校 他們有提起  我是如何做到這個位置的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你被新的檢察官  叫到他的辦公室...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.15,0:25:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 哈蘭·菲斯克·斯通  - 是的，斯通總檢察長
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.44,0:25:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓你去他的辦公室  讓你坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.40,0:25:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芝加哥有十多個空缺職位
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.99,0:25:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫率正在攀升  或許對調查局有利的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.20,0:25:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始填補這些空缺  努力復甦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.62,0:25:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有整理潛在犯罪嫌疑人的資料  經過國會的聽證會...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.16,0:25:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別激動 孩子  不是你叫我來開會的 是我叫你 坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.63,0:25:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡每個和你共事過的人都離開了  而且事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.01,0:26:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查局充斥著惡劣的氛圍  你也同意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.02,0:26:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並無冒犯之意  你似乎也沒有什麼社交
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.56,0:26:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有老婆 沒有女友  據我所知 甚至朋友都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.53,0:26:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還旁若無人地癡迷著  那亂七八糟的指紋系統
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.58,0:26:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我們可以將所有指紋都集中到這裡  這絕不會是亂七八糟的事 我可以保證
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.66,0:26:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這最多也就是一種投機學
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.42,0:26:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.25,0:26:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們為什麼都叫你「飛毛腿」？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.38,0:26:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰這麼叫我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.59,0:26:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們都這樣  不過很明顯是在你背後
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.18,0:26:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我10歲的時候給雜貨店送外賣  積攢了這個名聲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.35,0:26:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在我們街坊是速度最快的  這只是個外號
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.27,0:26:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定他們不是在說你說話的方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.15,0:26:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:27:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人 我希望你出任  調查局的局長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.08,0:27:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會接受這個職務 斯通先生  但有一些條件
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.59,0:27:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.25,0:27:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個調查局必須和政治獨立開  不能成為政治的代言人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.89,0:27:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人必須有大學文憑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.35,0:27:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任用的人必須體面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.22,0:27:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到升職的人必須有嫻熟的工作能力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.48,0:27:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這個調查局僅由您一人負責
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.57,0:27:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總檢察長
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.03,0:27:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換做其他條件  我也不會給你這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.70,0:27:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了 日安
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.54,0:27:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.87,0:27:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已決定  會從調查局剔除那些...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.09,0:28:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉迷於酒精的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.01,0:28:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信  當一個人成為調查局的一份子...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他必須規範自己的行為  不管官方還是非官方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.27,0:28:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以消除可能存在的  哪怕最小的批判聲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.94,0:28:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,批判他品行的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.15,0:28:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你叫什麼名字？  - 威廉姆斯 先生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.11,0:28:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 很高興見到你 威廉姆斯探員  - 您也是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.95,0:28:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.24,0:28:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡福利探員
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.95,0:28:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的任務是？  - 我正要前往堪薩斯城
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.45,0:28:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協助調查銀行搶劫犯弗蘭克·納什
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一項危險的任務  你回來以後...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.67,0:28:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會因你的努力工作得到嘉獎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.97,0:28:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯托克斯探員  你還是很喜歡留鬍子嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 女士們喜歡  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.85,0:28:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我是不是可以認為  女士們的意見比調查局的意見更重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.35,0:28:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.56,0:28:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長官
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.81,0:29:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你在警察局工作更合適...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相比在調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經為司法部和調查局效力了7年
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.66,0:29:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎跟你一樣長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.62,0:29:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.20,0:29:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在舊的調查局工作了7年  那個舊的已經不復存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.46,0:29:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.00,0:29:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就解雇了所有  不符合我要求的探員
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.30,0:29:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教育背景 身體條件...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.09,0:29:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是 忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.64,0:29:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了兩套  一樣的裁剪 不同花紋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.19,0:29:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有給你的兩套西裝  禮拜五就送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.19,0:29:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.11,0:29:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是鉑金的...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.66,0:29:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六顆鑽石  一顆星光藍寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.37,0:29:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太美了 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.21,0:29:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.21,0:30:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟整個街坊鄰居都說起了你  他們都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.88,0:30:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不該吃  我已經在增重了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是結實的體重  一個男人結結實實長點肉沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.39,0:30:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧  - 我真是太為你驕傲了 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.27,0:30:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我開始為你做一個冊子了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.40,0:30:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會把所有材料都收集進去  這只是個開始
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.74,0:30:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「約翰·胡佛被任命為  調查局的局長」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.29,0:30:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能讀讀這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.42,0:30:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為叔叔自豪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.27,0:31:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.23,0:31:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想介紹一下你  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.07,0:31:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 很高興見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.91,0:31:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你 勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.45,0:31:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想向你介紹克萊德·托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.12,0:31:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚剛從喬治華盛頓大學的法學院畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.08,0:31:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.29,0:31:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝賀你 托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 胡佛先生  我想你應該是我校最傑出的校友之一了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.96,0:31:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是的  我確實是從同個學校畢業的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.09,0:31:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡你的西服 托爾森先生  羅倫斯 你該學著點
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.72,0:31:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 這是在加芬克爾百貨商店定制的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.64,0:31:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.60,0:31:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有名片嗎 托爾森先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.81,0:31:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.44,0:31:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.82,0:31:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興見到你 勞倫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.20,0:32:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「良好的教育，被高度推薦  可以保證五年的工作時間」
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.87,0:32:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「家人在紐約 有剛出生的孩子」
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.71,0:32:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不用面試
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.38,0:32:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為紐約的家人還是剛出生的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.67,0:32:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪小姐 五年是不夠的  我們需要一個願意奉獻一生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.63,0:32:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有多少個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.30,0:32:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 320個被拒 21個面試者  - 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.72,0:32:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有收到一份  來自托爾森先生的申請嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.02,0:32:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.52,0:32:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 他的報告陳述道  他自信 優雅...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用詞精準
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.91,0:32:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身體條件沒問題  但並不希望做棘手的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.58,0:32:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是想為自己的個人法律實踐  積攢一些經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:32:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也沒有說起  願意在這裡工作多長時間...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.79,0:32:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只會讓就業更加投機
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.46,0:32:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.05,0:32:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有一封推薦信...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.93,0:32:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自戰爭部長的行政助理
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.18,0:33:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信裡提到托爾森先生...  對女人沒有特別的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.73,0:33:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再一次地 我們最好的一些探員  之所以如此優秀 是因為他們沒有家庭的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.24,0:33:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你是對的  安排面試
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.54,0:33:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道問題是什麼嗎  甘迪？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.75,0:33:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人 他們並不...  並不崇拜我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.88,0:33:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們當然崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.21,0:33:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這並不是比喻  我就是說 他們不崇拜我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如你可以坐在桌子後面  來進行面試...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.43,0:33:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是在辦公室走來走去  我可以讓他們崇拜你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.81,0:33:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.73,0:33:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 假如我有某位當權人士的  秘密資料...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.11,0:33:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有害的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.11,0:33:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅這些資料有悖我的意圖...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.87,0:34:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也不放心放在一般的資料一起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.95,0:34:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能拜託你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.79,0:34:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們或許可以保存一些絕密資料？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.79,0:34:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.67,0:34:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 甘迪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.89,0:34:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信息就是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.26,0:34:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信息保護我們1919年  不受共產主義分子危害
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.39,0:34:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自那以後 就由聯邦調查局  小心地收集 整理  維護
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.73,0:34:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪總檢察長辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.74,0:34:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都有這個壁爐嗎  還是後來安的？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.54,0:34:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來安的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.75,0:34:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那間屋子裝竊聽器是做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.54,0:34:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓我追查這些犯罪線索的  肯尼迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.67,0:34:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也照做了  勤勤懇懇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.84,0:34:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你會用這個壁爐嗎？  - 很少
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.30,0:35:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰聽過這個錄音？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.84,0:35:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經將資料封為  個人的 高度機密的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.68,0:35:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我才能取得這些資料
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.23,0:35:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生 我是讓你追查  真正的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相反地 你公然否認  有組織的犯罪的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.86,0:35:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還有這重大的恐嚇
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.36,0:35:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官  我只是服從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.20,0:35:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們竊聽了洛杉磯  一幢房子的地下室
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.62,0:35:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一群違法犯罪者聚會的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.70,0:35:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道一個東德的共產主義分子  會在那裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.29,0:35:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在那裡跟你的哥哥  也就是美國總統 上床？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.05,0:35:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要射殺那些探員  我是來保護你們倆的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.80,0:35:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.43,0:35:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.06,0:35:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這段資料公開...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.90,0:35:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會造成對你們兄弟倆領導能力  大面積的質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.19,0:36:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅這些  我還掌控我們國家最高的福利
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.90,0:36:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我該怎麼做呢 胡佛先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.70,0:36:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倘若我得幫你追查  你認為是威脅的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.75,0:36:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要您允許我有同樣的權力...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.58,0:36:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來追查我認為有重大威脅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.59,0:36:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這已經不是1920年了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.72,0:36:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道斯坦利·列維森是誰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個律師
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.10,0:36:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個白人 共產主義律師  組織著最高層...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.27,0:36:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括南方基督教領袖會議
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.19,0:36:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在他們的群體正在壯大
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們完全自給自足...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的領導權已經公然  危及到我們的部門
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.28,0:36:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了我發過來的備忘嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.20,0:36:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.45,0:36:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪先生 我在這裡寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.62,0:36:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們宣稱我們是...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「不能給哪怕最滔天最極惡的犯罪定罪」
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:36:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還「在壓力下動搖」
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.38,0:36:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「因為部門的複雜性和義務」  白紙黑字印出來
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.84,0:37:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就在這《華盛頓郵報》上  - 你就受不了一點點的批評？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.72,0:37:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這取決於批評的目的了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.14,0:37:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們正在聚集一股很客觀的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.47,0:37:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們有優先權  單單關注自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.52,0:37:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在試圖煽動叛亂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顯然 他們看上去更多的批評你的部門  而不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.19,0:37:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共產主義有了新的局面了  埃德加 這件事不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.15,0:37:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共產主義更多地是海外的威脅  不是國內的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.16,0:37:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪先生  遠在你出生以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.83,0:37:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從一位叫米切爾·帕爾默先生口中  聽到了一模一樣的說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.33,0:37:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道最後是什麼  讓他改變自己的想法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.17,0:37:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一枚炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.84,0:37:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如他在1919年的那天  在他的椅子上多坐五分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就只能發現他的手指頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我不想讓這些事  發生在你和你哥哥身上
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.02,0:37:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒理由  讓我們都得不到我們想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:38:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以在兩個前線都發動戰爭  你明白我的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.90,0:38:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以走了 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.70,0:38:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.12,0:38:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把副本留下給我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.80,0:38:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 也可以讓你哥哥看看這些
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.88,0:38:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他知道  我自己也留了一份存檔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.87,0:38:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您4點的面試者到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.12,0:38:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 甘迪  讓他進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.87,0:39:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐吧 托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.38,0:39:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 胡佛先生 謝謝您給我這次機會  - 請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.26,0:39:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 請坐  - 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.76,0:39:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的申請材料有幾個問題  托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.39,0:39:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且不提其實你並不...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.47,0:39:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,符合調查局的條件...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.44,0:39:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有要保護美國人民的忠心...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.23,0:39:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以美國自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.44,0:39:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須告訴你的是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.03,0:39:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是給你的個人法律實踐  發工資的地方 托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎 托爾森先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.45,0:39:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.62,0:39:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這鍛煉是所有探員都要求的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.88,0:39:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們所有的探員  都需要有最好的身體條件
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.97,0:39:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須對公眾之敵百發百中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.47,0:39:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以您經常做什麼來健身？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.64,0:40:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯臥撐 仰臥起坐 還有下蹲運動
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.94,0:40:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你整理一下窗簾吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.40,0:40:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以開點窗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.15,0:40:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運動之後我喜歡來一些新鮮空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.78,0:40:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.49,0:40:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜歡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我或許在簡歷方面不如他人...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.12,0:40:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其他方面  我的忠誠度遠遠超過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.92,0:40:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並未因為這個工作而說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.75,0:40:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像其他人  是的 我希望做法律實踐...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.38,0:40:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也可以做其他事  倘若有不錯的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.51,0:40:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.56,0:40:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有道理 托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.19,0:40:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.29,0:41:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這袖子看上去長度正好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.46,0:41:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到兩條領帶給你選
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.17,0:41:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條更加時髦...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.54,0:41:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更好的搭配這套西服  包括剪裁和材質
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.25,0:41:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得有點太扎眼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太扎眼？好吧  所以我還給你找了個後備
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.84,0:41:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 這條更有領導人氣質 更...  - 更含蓄些 我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.72,0:41:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們留著這條作候補吧  謝謝你 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.73,0:41:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是約翰·胡佛先生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我 有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.36,0:41:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有位約翰·胡佛先生  在我們這裡信用度很差
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.65,0:41:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.36,0:41:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不是我 我保證
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.16,0:41:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我母親叫我埃德加 我侄女叫我J.E.  我簽名都簽約翰·E 而不是約翰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.12,0:41:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如您是托爾森先生的朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.04,0:41:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再選一個名字 重新申請一次
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.75,0:41:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.21,0:41:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.89,0:42:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 甘迪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.64,0:42:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？你不喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.06,0:42:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生  堪薩斯城發生了一起慘案
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.03,0:42:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有我們自己的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.74,0:42:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡福利探員？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.33,0:42:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他來！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.29,0:42:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1930年 共產主義分子危機捲土重來
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.37,0:42:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但同時有大蕭條的影響  產生新的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.79,0:42:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀行搶劫 盜車 綁架
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.67,0:42:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不幸的是 對於共產主義  美國並未打壓
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.13,0:42:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們激發出了美國黑幫
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.39,0:42:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些窮凶極惡的 持械的犯罪分子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對社會和文明力量的挑戰  不會再得到縱容
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.35,0:42:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「瘋狂莫蘭」和阿爾·卡彭是我們的頭號公敵  （前者是禁酒令時期芝加哥的黑幫 後者是意大利裔美國黑幫）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.40,0:42:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你們周圍  他們無處不在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.69,0:43:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須重申  調查局會是大家的保護傘
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.45,0:43:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它屬於人民  它就和家裡的電話一樣就在你們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.04,0:43:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了你們的幫助...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.29,0:43:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,華納兄弟影業為大家呈現有聲電影
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.04,0:43:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·卡格尼飾演頭號公敵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.01,0:43:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 為什麼 你...  - 啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.22,0:43:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又開始說那些願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.43,0:43:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你可以找到你更喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.18,0:43:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即將登陸各大院線
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.81,0:43:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.73,0:43:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天 一場犯罪  讓一切都步入了正軌
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.07,0:43:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道是哪件事嗎  瓊斯先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.99,0:43:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.49,0:43:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止 誰是20世紀最有名的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.83,0:43:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喬·麥卡錫？  （約瑟夫·雷蒙德·麥卡錫，美國政治家，反共產主義者）
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.58,0:43:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥卡錫就是個機會主義者...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.09,0:43:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是個愛國者 瓊斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.88,0:44:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前為止  誰是20世紀最有名的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.47,0:44:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最有名？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.77,0:44:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是您？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.40,0:44:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他的惡名  取決於他是什麼行業的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.90,0:44:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天上飛的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.24,0:44:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是查爾斯·林德伯格了  （美國飛行員 首個單人不著陸飛越大西洋的人）
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.51,0:44:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.72,0:44:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查爾斯·林德伯格的小孩  被人從家中綁架了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.84,0:44:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從特雷敦派警官過去  我會乘頭班火車趕到
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.56,0:44:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.77,0:45:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查爾斯·林德伯格...  他的孩子被綁架了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.61,0:45:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.07,0:45:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得把孩子安全帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.58,0:45:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 母親 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.21,0:45:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當1932年的那個早晨  我們到達林德伯格家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.09,0:45:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正開始一項  即將永遠改變調查局的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.59,0:45:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上我們收到來自賓州鐵路的  威爾·羅傑斯的消息...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.06,0:45:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛總統 羅斯福州長 海關...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.14,0:45:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有美國郵政 和童子軍
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.06,0:45:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們所有人  趕緊離開那泥地
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.81,0:45:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這是踩踏證據  快！走開！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.65,0:45:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡什麼都沒有 我們檢查過了  沒有可以辨認的腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.78,0:45:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎罪犯在鞋子上綁了布
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.15,0:45:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你不覺得印記的大小  也會有點價值嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.99,0:45:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎麼爬上去的？  窗子和牆上是不是也有證據？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.49,0:45:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在100碼之外發現了梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.62,0:45:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們把它放進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.25,0:45:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你動過它了？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.58,0:45:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 安全保管起見
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.33,0:46:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你啊 施瓦茲科夫先生  你徹徹底底污染了這個犯罪現場
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.50,0:46:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在可以高抬貴腳趕緊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.76,0:46:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼權利來這裡？  你叫...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.22,0:46:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J·埃德加·胡佛  調查局局長
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.01,0:46:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們由胡佛總統指派  來保障這次調查
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.18,0:46:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統已經授權我們可以  查看所有的文件和證據
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.44,0:46:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生 你看看沒問題  但新澤西可不是總統的私人領土
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.44,0:46:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格先生呢？  我想要聽聽他的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.19,0:46:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 林德伯格先生在後面  - 您先請
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.45,0:46:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一夜沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.28,0:46:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格先生親自下來見了我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.49,0:46:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和我握手  表達了他對我們年輕的調查局的感謝和信任
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.29,0:46:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他從五尺高的地方摔下來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.46,0:46:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.84,0:46:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架犯  手裡還抱著孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.47,0:46:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是推測
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.34,0:46:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格先生 倘若這個梯子在  這個人爬上去的時候已經開裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.18,0:46:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它肯定已經塌了  你看 這是個失算
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.14,0:47:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它本來可以承受一個成人的重量爬上去  但無法承受一個成人加一個孩子爬下來
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.85,0:47:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有別的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.90,0:47:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要贖金的字條呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.98,0:47:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.82,0:47:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣光著手摸這張紙？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.53,0:47:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們檢查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.74,0:47:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你那麼喜歡的指紋在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.29,0:47:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它遞過來吧 施瓦茲科夫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.25,0:47:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫科內爾·施瓦茲科夫
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.38,0:47:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「準備好五萬美元」  ready（準備）拼成了R-E-D-Y
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.38,0:47:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我們會告訴你地點」  拼成了W-E-R-E；「把錢送到...」
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.17,0:47:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,money（錢）拼成了M-O-N-Y
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.68,0:47:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「警告你不許聲張消息或者通知警方」
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.01,0:47:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「指示的所有信件都要簽字」  拼成了S-I-N-G，「singnature」
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.69,0:47:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紙有三個孔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.86,0:47:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要這封信和那個梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.11,0:47:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有這個管轄權  我們已經給你看了你想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.44,0:47:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你可以走了  - 林德伯格先生 請...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.03,0:47:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生 謝謝你  你也看得到 一切都安排妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.58,0:47:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.54,0:47:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你抽空 林德伯格先生
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.04,0:48:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.84,0:48:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 我很擔心他的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.34,0:48:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相比我們 他更信任當地警方
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.85,0:48:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他覺得我們都是傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.47,0:48:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也會聽他們的  他會去跟綁架犯談判
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.56,0:48:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛總統今天早上給我打電話  告訴我孩子被綁架了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.77,0:48:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓我做我權力以內的任何事  去解決案件
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.11,0:48:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你們是否知道  調查局的所有權力是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.24,0:48:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有法律保護 沒有槍支  沒有權利來逮捕？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.37,0:48:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.37,0:48:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席 我強烈建議通過這項林德伯格法案
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.12,0:48:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓綁架成為一項國家級的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.67,0:48:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應當立即把國家所有的指紋  都送來我辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.84,0:48:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就可以建立一個中央檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.18,0:48:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我們的探員武裝起來  讓他們有機會戰鬥...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.51,0:49:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和那些最危險的  持衝鋒鎗的人作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.52,0:49:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國歷史上最危險的罪犯之一
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.64,0:49:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要敦促你們  為了小林迪這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.23,0:49:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為連他都可以被綁架  那誰家的孩子還會是安全的？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.69,0:49:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我們無法幫助他安全回家  那我們還有什麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.01,0:49:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從當地機關送來的指紋...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.31,0:49:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自全國各地 開始湧來  最終 我們有了這個中央系統
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.69,0:49:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 埃德加？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.65,0:49:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芝加哥送來的最後一批指紋
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.07,0:49:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我們的新總統  跟我安排了一次見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.57,0:50:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道有謠言說  要重組調查局？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.37,0:50:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的我聽到了相似的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.17,0:50:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.96,0:50:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 你還記不記得  我們給他的妻子建立的那個文件？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.26,0:50:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯福夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.01,0:50:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.76,0:50:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能給我拷貝一份嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.76,0:50:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.27,0:50:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 甘迪
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.76,0:51:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格是讓一群罪犯來找他兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.22,0:51:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以離開桌子了 加裡森調查員  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.68,0:51:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.89,0:51:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他甚至得到了來自阿爾·卡彭的邀請  來幫他付贖金
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.15,0:51:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是最後 他雇了一個怪人  叫約翰·康登的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.23,0:51:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人在報紙上登廣告  以此跟綁架犯交流
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.65,0:51:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那康登也是個罪犯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.24,0:51:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定也不是什麼法律的代言人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.79,0:51:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要這樣做？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.46,0:51:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一個母親就能重新找回她的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.54,0:51:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以知道  美國人民很感謝你...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.84,0:51:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賜予他們膽量和氣魄
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.13,0:51:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎麼知道  綁架者與跟你寫這些信的是同一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.60,0:51:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有標記 跟原來的信一樣  不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.69,0:51:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 林德伯格先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.69,0:51:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次我很輕率地...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.86,0:52:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把那些標記給了其他人看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.20,0:52:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不確定  他們是否值得信任了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.37,0:52:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定任何人是否值得信任了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.00,0:52:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會拿你收到的這些信去鑒定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.04,0:52:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來確認他們是來自同一個人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.21,0:52:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正當林德伯格先生  把自己的信任交給這些惡棍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.71,0:52:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始發展一件  讓罪犯無法戰勝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.39,0:52:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用世上任何槍都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.22,0:52:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們 請離開這個房間  清理桌面 現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.52,0:52:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去哪裡抽煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.85,0:52:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不關我的事  別在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.60,0:52:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 奧斯本先生 告訴我們你的需要  - 明亮的燈光 一個顯微鏡...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.90,0:52:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度量工具 放大鏡  還有一個投影儀
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.57,0:52:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你擁有這間調查局的所有資源  不要害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.70,0:52:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個地區製造商的紙張樣品
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.99,0:52:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯本先生 這位是托爾森  協助奧斯本先生 不管他有什麼需要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.78,0:52:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以百分百斷定  這些信出自同一人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.96,0:52:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.88,0:52:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們 請離開 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.67,0:53:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們是不是應該告訴檢察官？  - 好讓他第三次拒絕我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.05,0:53:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 掛個牌子 像這個一樣  - 你想說什麼，「禁止入內」？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.97,0:53:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「調查局技術實驗室」
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.72,0:53:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻好 釘在牆上  如果有人想要撤了它 他還得花點力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.89,0:53:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是時候我們至少有  犯罪分子沒有的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.06,0:53:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾技巧？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.27,0:53:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是科學 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.98,0:53:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墨水不同  但筆跡吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.28,0:53:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰在和康登先生交涉  就是那個寫第一張字條的人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.24,0:53:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者康登寫了所有的字條
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.37,0:53:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格正計劃讓康登  來送那些贖金
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.16,0:53:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 或許已經送去了  - 聯繫內部稅收部門
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.79,0:53:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們去林德伯格家  我要讓所有的鈔票都做好標記
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.80,0:53:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.05,0:53:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了嗎 胡佛先生？  我兩點半還有課
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.05,0:53:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你不用去了  你的薪水將會翻倍
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.30,0:53:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在為國家做事了 奧斯本先生  祝賀你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.73,0:53:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.57,0:54:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到錢了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.99,0:54:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒見到孩子之前  我不能把錢帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.42,0:54:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證沒有警察
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.75,0:54:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.59,0:54:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停！快停！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.27,0:54:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.14,0:54:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們抓住我那就會了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.06,0:54:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他們只想要這個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.61,0:54:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我被抓 會被判30年  這會毀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.15,0:54:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.78,0:54:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.03,0:54:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個送信的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.16,0:54:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果孩子已經死了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.24,0:54:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子死了的話我是不是就完了？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.54,0:55:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果孩子已經死了  那我們還見面幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.21,0:55:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿到錢再登一個廣告
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.88,0:55:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果贖金必須支付  我們需要追蹤這些鈔票
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.39,0:55:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們叫來了國稅局的人  出於他的考慮 我們必須強迫他如此
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.73,0:55:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得黃金證明這種東西  早就已經不流通了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.73,0:55:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是我們的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.23,0:55:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會讓這些鈔票更有辨識度
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.28,0:55:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要這些錢  我只想要我兒子回來
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.40,0:55:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不僅僅關乎您的兒子  林德伯格先生
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.53,0:55:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這些綁架犯逍遙法外  這個國家就沒有一個孩子是安全的了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.58,0:55:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什麼我已經組成了一支26人的隊伍  由特別探員西斯科帶領
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.54,0:55:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如他們發現你有參與此事  我會永遠見不到我兒子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.55,0:55:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格先生  我們不會有任何超前的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.63,0:55:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到您的孩子平安回到母親的懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.09,0:55:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向您保證
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.94,0:56:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小查爾斯·A·林德伯格的綁架案  是一場悲劇...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.11,0:56:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅對於科內爾和林德伯格夫人  還有整個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.86,0:56:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他從家中被綁架這件事  對整個美國都是挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.11,0:56:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梯子 綁架案的唯一線索  是自己手工造的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.03,0:56:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓林德伯格案件的一切進展  作為新的力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.12,0:56:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消滅一切骯髒  不僅僅是這次放肆的綁架案
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.16,0:56:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括所有的綁架和犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.80,0:56:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 醫生！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.21,0:56:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告訴你六小時之內不要打開
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.47,0:56:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.77,0:56:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他談下來2萬
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.11,0:56:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇讓他高興點 而不是省錢  我不想讓他生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.57,0:56:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.99,0:56:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證六小時之內不打開這個
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.74,0:56:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你的 我沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.83,0:57:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「孩子在奈麗號船上  是一艘小船 28尺長」
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.46,0:57:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「有兩個人在船上 他們是無辜的」
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.67,0:57:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「船在荷森內克海灘和  伊莉莎白島旁邊的蓋荷鎮之間」
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.84,0:57:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在楠塔基特 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.85,0:57:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船裡面有什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.22,0:57:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有船
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.77,0:57:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格沒有信任我們  他要按自己的方式來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.60,0:57:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰能怪他呢  當時沒有人尊重我們調查局
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.36,0:57:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生  我們一直在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.23,0:57:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.45,0:57:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該走了 加裡森調查員  現在
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.53,0:57:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總檢察長已經授權了  你的竊聽器
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.87,0:57:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 甘迪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.54,0:57:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 你確定要這麼做嗎？  你要是這麼做了 事情就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.88,0:57:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我證明我是對的以後  我們可以再次避免國家陷入革命
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.84,0:57:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歷史會記住我們的 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.67,0:57:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但假如你錯了...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.05,0:57:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歷史也會記住這是一次  因為小的恩怨產生的非法行為
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.55,0:58:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我們的名聲是小事嗎  托爾森？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.68,0:58:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不 我...  - 那就去訂這些電線
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.81,0:58:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們能不能晚飯時候討論一下？  - 在你訂了電線以後
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.44,0:58:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.58,0:58:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,局長已經在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.81,0:58:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您請
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.80,0:59:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.80,0:59:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 去哈維餐館？  - 不 去白宮
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.44,0:59:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在經歷大蕭條
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.69,0:59:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被史上最嚴重的戰爭  壓得喘不過氣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.66,0:59:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要更多的權力來保護  但 每次有新的總統上任
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.66,0:59:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查局的未來 以及我個人的職位  都要被打上問號
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.33,0:59:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 總統先生可以見你了  - 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.18,1:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧 請坐 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.51,1:00:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是一樣的戲碼  他們讓我一直等
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.81,1:00:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想像我會緊張流汗  然後他們就擺明自己才是老大 我是單打獨鬥
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.02,1:00:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.82,1:00:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給他看了那些記錄副本嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.86,1:00:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他不想看  這很特殊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.99,1:00:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想讓我口頭告訴他
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.37,1:00:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你是怎麼說的？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.24,1:00:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就直接跟他說  我們不曾想到會抓到羅斯福夫人...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.54,1:00:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在一個知名的共產主義分子的臥室裡
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.12,1:00:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像是很親密
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.71,1:00:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要他指示該如何繼續調查
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.88,1:00:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓他知道  他還是有盟友的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.51,1:00:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他要求你自己辭職之前
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.68,1:00:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.10,1:00:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說完以後  他就把文件推到一邊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.06,1:00:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他根本不關心
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.48,1:00:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 美國的總統害怕了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.48,1:01:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他害怕你？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.23,1:01:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕潛在的來自國外的侵略
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.99,1:01:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來兩杯你們最好的香檳
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.74,1:01:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.08,1:01:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你開始喝酒了？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.75,1:01:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是慶祝 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.54,1:01:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 我覺得我可以  任何事都信任你 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.29,1:01:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很樂意這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.30,1:01:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統簽署了一份密令
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.13,1:01:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給予我更多的監視權...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.60,1:01:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密監視共產主義分子和激進者的權利  不需要任何授權
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.06,1:01:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這合法？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.27,1:01:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候 你需要過界一些...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.85,1:01:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來保護國家的安全  是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.44,1:01:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保證我沒有聽錯  我還和國務卿赫爾證實了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.07,1:01:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說 我引用一下  「去吧 調查那些口交的傢伙們」
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.66,1:01:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好粗俗啊  - 同意
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.12,1:01:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.46,1:01:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.17,1:02:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.30,1:02:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一個人  理解現在什麼是危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.97,1:02:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.43,1:02:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個我可以信任的人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.14,1:02:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查局的副局長
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.14,1:02:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你在你現在的位置  只做了差不多12個月
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.77,1:02:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將近18個月了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.81,1:02:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒理解我說的 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.40,1:02:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你做我的二把手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.20,1:02:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不適應那些聚光燈 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.49,1:02:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.79,1:02:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白嗎？  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.67,1:02:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個條件
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.25,1:02:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管這一天是好是壞  不管我們是否同意過...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.42,1:02:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠都要一起吃午飯和晚餐
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.18,1:02:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會同意其他的條件
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.19,1:03:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 停車
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.65,1:03:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 離玫瑰山只有半英里了  - 等不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.06,1:03:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歐威爾！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.95,1:03:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終 孩子的屍體被發現...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.58,1:03:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在林德伯格家視野範圍內
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.08,1:04:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屍體已經變黑
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.08,1:04:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左腿膝蓋以下都不見了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.67,1:04:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭骨上有明顯的骨折
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.09,1:04:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他頭上受到了強大的外力擊打  我幾個月前就告訴他了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.43,1:04:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在爬下去的時候肯定摔了  手裡抱著孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.77,1:04:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都有罪 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.19,1:04:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們如此縱容無法無天的行為  讓它們變成窮凶極惡的犯罪
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.78,1:04:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的手上沾滿了孩子的鮮血  埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.45,1:04:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手上
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.79,1:04:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 母親
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.51,1:05:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架案六周以後
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.52,1:05:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國會通過了林德伯格法案
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.52,1:05:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把綁架定為國家級犯罪
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.44,1:05:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了拘捕的權利  以及攜帶槍支的權利
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.48,1:05:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我繼續聚集著  全國最好的科學頭腦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.78,1:05:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他是世界上最好的  木材鑒定專家
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.54,1:05:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如你是世界上唯一有某種興趣的人  成為專家很容易
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.58,1:05:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他聲稱從木頭的斷面  他可以鑒定出...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.08,1:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 和醫生屍檢獲得的信息一樣多  - 這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.42,1:05:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有 呃 社交困難
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.01,1:05:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他精神有問題 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.34,1:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過跟你一樣瘋狂罷了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.51,1:05:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這本應該只是暫時的  胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.43,1:05:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如你想要繼續你這福爾摩斯的遊戲...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.77,1:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你覺得我們還能去哪？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.52,1:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議你去國會解決這個問題
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.61,1:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 那就照你說的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.07,1:05:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就告訴人們 只是因為無法負擔實驗室  我們就不能解決這些案件
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.15,1:05:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而總檢察長不願意我們佔用他的休息室
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.24,1:06:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行吧 把你的這些科學實驗搬出去
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.87,1:06:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 馬上
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.21,1:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續工作
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.46,1:06:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托爾森  幫我接到總統的電話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.88,1:06:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡性犯罪的日益嚴重  像一群狼一樣從一個州遊蕩到另一個州
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.93,1:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為真正武裝侵蝕美國的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.76,1:06:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須智取這些犯罪分子  不論是國外還是國內的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.68,1:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們有化學藥品來製造炸彈  我們就也需要化學藥品來追蹤他們
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.81,1:06:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須有世界上最先進的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.73,1:06:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我們想要成為世界上最安全的國家
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.32,1:06:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生們 請不要 哪怕就一刻  失去我們的視野和目標
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.07,1:06:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護忠誠的國民
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.70,1:06:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴犯罪分子  不管他有什麼托詞
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.74,1:06:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他如何扭曲  如何在泥濘中蠕動
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.96,1:06:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人可以避免
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.09,1:06:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.92,1:06:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.09,1:07:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你的機構已經是華盛頓  財政支持最多的機構之一了 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.18,1:07:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 的確...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.85,1:07:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們去年的劫車 劫銀行的案件  恢復到了650萬美元的高度
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.93,1:07:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的預算只有200萬
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.56,1:07:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像華盛頓的其他部門  我們看上去還掙了點嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.28,1:07:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能用數字來  衡量我們的成功...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.95,1:07:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括「帥哥弗洛伊德」（銀行搶劫者）  「娃娃臉尼爾森」（銀行搶劫者）「機關鎗凱利」（黑幫）這些惡棍
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.20,1:07:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他很多的惡人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.49,1:07:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生 你把調查局的經費  花在了廣告方面 這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.92,1:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不允許任何形式的廣告
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.46,1:07:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你參與了 比如說  廣播節目的製作 還有漫畫書
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.14,1:07:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過幾次政府官員的電台節目
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.80,1:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的照片似乎經常跟他們出現在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.31,1:07:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們強調過  拒絕給他們任何支持...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.36,1:07:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些和他們的產品無關的東西  不提供建議 技術 或是任何東西
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.24,1:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這條廣告說  廣播是...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.61,1:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「最真實的反映官方記錄中...」
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.99,1:08:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「根據聯邦調查局的真實案件改編」
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.91,1:08:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「週六晚上8點檔」
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.13,1:08:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生  你到底有何資質...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.84,1:08:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,處於你現在所在調查局的領導地位？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.51,1:08:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的資質？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.92,1:08:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在司法部工作了19年  19年
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.97,1:08:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中12年是調查局局長
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.68,1:08:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那段時間  你有沒有親自逮捕犯罪分子？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.02,1:08:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了調查  我同時主管好幾件案子
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.61,1:08:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這沒有回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.19,1:08:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漫畫書裡有你拿著機關鎗  逮捕犯罪分子的情景 這只是編造？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.83,1:08:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負責了幾千次的逮捕
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.58,1:08:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你承認那些都是編的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.46,1:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上 不是你把約翰·迪林傑  打倒並抓獲的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.51,1:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是博維斯探員  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.39,1:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負責了所有的這些調查...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.85,1:09:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但的確 我個人並未做出任何拘捕
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.24,1:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.24,1:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們投票決定吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.87,1:09:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這些拿走
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.42,1:09:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情不太順利啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.00,1:09:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們拚命工作  結果落得被政治攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.92,1:09:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想要怎樣 案件沒法解決？  他幹嘛跟我作對？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.59,1:09:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去開始調查麥克凱勒參議員
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.84,1:09:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安排四個探員同時調查
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.80,1:09:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道他丟的垃圾裡都有什麼  我要他每天吃晚飯的照片
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.93,1:09:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要上這輛車 你可以走回去
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.77,1:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 我們要吃午飯的  我們不論如何都是一起吃午飯的 記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.44,1:10:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面的時候  你就那樣離開丟下我一人
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.44,1:10:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給自己作偽證了 埃德加  還是個很容易被識破的謊言
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.94,1:10:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還要繼續這些  我都不敢說事情會變得多糟糕
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.11,1:10:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把博維斯探員找出來  馬上把他降職 或者最好是炒了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.16,1:10:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把抓到約翰·迪林傑的人炒了  這會是重大人力損失
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.00,1:10:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他就餘生都在辦公桌前度過吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.41,1:10:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他想保住飯碗  他最好離重要文件遠點 開車
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.22,1:10:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我還能信任誰
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.89,1:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有您了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.48,1:10:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有您了 母親
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.65,1:10:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我唯一擁有的 保佑我安全的人  你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.19,1:10:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 媽媽  讓我帶你去看醫生
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.57,1:10:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單地檢查一下沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.49,1:10:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.83,1:10:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.83,1:11:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信念 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.84,1:11:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信念
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.84,1:11:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要像一朵小花一樣枯萎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.34,1:11:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要堅強
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.76,1:11:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 母親
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.64,1:11:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.11,1:11:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如國會更喜歡力量  而不是頭腦和智慧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.32,1:11:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們更需要的是  一個武裝起來的美國英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.57,1:11:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我會冒著生命危險  做到兩者兼備
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.54,1:11:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行動
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.87,1:11:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.33,1:11:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住！政府探員！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.51,1:11:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次逮捕應該是我來！
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.39,1:11:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閃開
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.56,1:12:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡佩斯先生 你被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.23,1:12:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛親自出馬啊  我要出名了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.90,1:12:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他銬起來
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.66,1:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許動 麥漢先生
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.74,1:12:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放倒它
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.87,1:12:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行動
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.72,1:12:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本內特先生 你被逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.26,1:12:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾文·卡佩斯說他不能被活捉  但我們一槍都沒開就抓住了他
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.73,1:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼跟你說吧 他抖得跟篩子似的  聲音 手 還有膝蓋
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.73,1:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還在托雷多逮捕了哈利·坎貝爾  在曼哈頓逮捕了本內特？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.94,1:12:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有在加州逮捕了威廉·麥漢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.65,1:12:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我要再次申明  這絕對地...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.32,1:12:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是團隊合作的結果  而不是我個人的成就
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.71,1:13:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 看看這個  我們做了這個麥片盒子
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.46,1:13:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「梅爾文·博維斯  抓住迪林傑的調查局探員」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.51,1:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯繫麥片製造商  讓他們知道...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.22,1:13:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 政府官員的電台節目
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.80,1:13:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們必須把以後所有的盒子印成  「前調查局探員」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.64,1:13:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下 克萊德  我給你念段東西
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.98,1:13:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「還有8天」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.94,1:13:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「雖然可笑 但最親愛的人的臉  就要消失了」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.15,1:13:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「最清楚地記住了你的眼睛...」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.03,1:13:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「眼神裡有挑逗的笑意  還有那最柔軟的一點...」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.41,1:13:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「就在你嘴唇的東北角  正對我的雙唇」
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.16,1:13:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.75,1:13:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一封來自羅蕾娜·西科克的信
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.54,1:13:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個有口臭的白宮報道員  寫給羅斯福太太的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.30,1:13:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  那你要拿這個怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.34,1:13:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怎麼樣  我指控過她和男人有外遇...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.09,1:14:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這位馬臉老阿姨  要和口臭小姐有一腿了！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.35,1:14:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個女人！你相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.19,1:14:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 打擾了 胡佛先生  他們要你去實驗室一趟
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.53,1:14:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 甘迪 告訴他們  我馬上就下去 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.03,1:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們等會兒再處理這個
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.82,1:14:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到馬 克萊德  我這個週末會去德爾馬爾（加州）一趟
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.33,1:14:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在考慮度一個簡短的假期
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.50,1:14:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你會不會樂意跟我一起去
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.83,1:14:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還從沒看過賽馬比賽呢  埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.21,1:14:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.46,1:14:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就對你說啊 如果我賭輸了  他們會幫我付這錢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.88,1:14:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那如果你贏了呢？  - 那還是他們付錢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.72,1:14:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這有什麼刺激的？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.97,1:14:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陽光灑在看台上  酒店房間 好的服務...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.02,1:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有餐廳 但最重要的是  克萊德 是和你同去的人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.06,1:14:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 和我一起去吧  - 我很樂意
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.32,1:14:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我會讓甘迪  安排好一切
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.65,1:14:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我不能現在去  但或許過兩個月 等我存點錢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.07,1:15:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 費用都我包了 克萊德  - 埃德加 這可不行
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.58,1:15:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 你為我做了這麼多事  也為了調查局 就當是我謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.00,1:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我會不會覺得舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.34,1:15:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣告訴你吧  我會定一個套間 有相鄰的臥室
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.38,1:15:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是兩個人分開訂房間  這樣就節省多了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.34,1:15:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成交
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.18,1:15:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼新發現嗎 科勒先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.10,1:15:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到  這裡有幾種木頭
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.60,1:15:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,松木 樺木 冷杉 還有  如果你仔細看還能看到...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.10,1:15:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝  - 托爾森先生
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.44,1:15:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每種木材都有自己獨特的內部紋理  年輪和梔...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.28,1:15:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有獨特的外在紋理  是機器打磨原木的時候形成的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.28,1:15:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些說明了製造梯子的工具
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.87,1:15:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是 這些能如何幫我們找到  綁架犯呢 科勒先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.12,1:15:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要更多經費
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.91,1:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 更多經費？為了幹嘛？  - 郵資
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.58,1:15:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要給東岸的每家廠子寫信
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.25,1:15:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他們的刀片切口是否和這個吻合
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.80,1:15:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.63,1:16:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把每個廠家的信息寫進報告  並把追蹤的所有線索畫成地圖
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.97,1:16:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回到紐約以後  我要你有點料可以報告
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.47,1:16:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.65,1:16:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他們之前的共產主義激進分子一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.99,1:16:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑幫也沒落了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.65,1:16:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在終於 孩子們夢想  成為聯邦調查局探員
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.08,1:16:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.92,1:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.76,1:16:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在洗澡 可以留個言嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.09,1:16:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡根本不能洗澡
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.69,1:17:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧波兒小姐！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.03,1:17:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生 我在想  你願不願意加入我的警力組
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.91,1:17:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 鄧波兒小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.45,1:17:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如你願意變成一名體面的女特工  再親一親我
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.50,1:17:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你的妻子會不會允許了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.63,1:17:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你看  我還和我媽媽住在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.88,1:17:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.63,1:17:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看這邊！  - 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.05,1:17:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微笑一個 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.31,1:17:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生 我們需要一個說明...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.39,1:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您喜歡這部電影嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.02,1:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.40,1:17:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您先請 母親
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.41,1:17:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去俱樂部嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.91,1:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我們把媽媽送回賓館
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.64,1:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們和阿妮塔·科爾比（演員）一桌
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.06,1:18:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂拉·羅傑斯和她的女兒金吉爾（演員）  也問了她們能不能一起
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.53,1:18:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多益善
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.24,1:18:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑斯小姐 很高興見到你  這應該就是你的母親了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.45,1:18:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.62,1:18:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是J·埃德加·胡佛 這位是克萊德·托爾森  阿妮塔 很高興見到你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.21,1:18:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子彈是從後腦勺射入...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.30,1:18:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從前面大概臉頰的地方穿出
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.92,1:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多數人沒有認識到的是  其實流血很少
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.47,1:18:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,子彈產生的熱量  會把入射產生的傷口密封起來
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.30,1:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以其實犯罪現場比你們電影中  描繪的要正常多了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.27,1:19:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有小林迪  您親眼看到這個孩子了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.48,1:19:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一些案件的細節...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.69,1:19:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好還是不要透露給  你們這些如此優雅的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.53,1:19:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能讓你們傷心流淚  但我向你們保證 我們仍舊在查案
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.58,1:19:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在巴黎見到了林德伯格一家  都差點認不出了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.83,1:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.00,1:19:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有正義才能讓他們  重新找回生活的意義
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.67,1:19:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟你們說說已經找到的機密線索  你們要發誓保密
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.72,1:19:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.01,1:19:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贖金中金色標記的鈔票已經浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.64,1:19:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜是在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.51,1:19:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.18,1:19:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在布朗克斯（紐約）  出現了三次
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.56,1:19:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個店主都說...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.60,1:19:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈔票都來自一個  有尖下巴和德國口音的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.36,1:19:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.36,1:19:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算全世界都仰慕  沒有愛 還是會少了一塊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.36,1:19:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.57,1:19:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說 可以溫暖你的床
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.70,1:19:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是國家的人 科爾比小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.75,1:20:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國家對我的讚許  已經是無上的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.46,1:20:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不管如何 你的床鋪還是冰冷
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.71,1:20:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生  您是否考慮和我跳一支舞？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.34,1:20:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.47,1:20:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是跳支舞
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.60,1:20:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會跳舞的吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.47,1:20:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這倒是我還未掌握的技能
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.19,1:20:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不早了 是嗎  托爾森？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.48,1:20:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比現在更好的了  這是我最愛的歌 來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.36,1:20:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該走了  我們還有很多工作要做
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.03,1:20:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們...我們...  我們明天還有很多工作
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.41,1:20:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕沒有時間跳舞了  我們很忙的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.33,1:20:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.79,1:20:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真誠地道歉
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.25,1:20:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托爾森 我們現在走吧  非常感謝你們
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.37,1:20:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.00,1:20:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.30,1:20:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.26,1:20:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.47,1:20:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡跳舞 母親
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.43,1:20:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不喜歡跳...  - 埃德加 去照照鏡子
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.56,1:21:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按照醫生教的方法說話  小飛毛腿
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.78,1:21:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以說...說...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.37,1:21:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以準確地 清晰地 用詞準確地說話
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.95,1:21:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以準確地...  清晰地 用詞準確地說話
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.42,1:21:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我工作嫻熟 出眾  做了了不起的事
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.55,1:21:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...  媽 我不喜歡跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.64,1:21:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說我不喜歡和女人跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.56,1:21:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是時候讓你知道這個了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.68,1:21:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這很丟人  我不喜歡丟人
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.48,1:21:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.98,1:21:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得巴頓·品克斯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.19,1:21:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記得
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.94,1:21:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的父親是鐘錶匠
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.66,1:21:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他比我小10歲  你叫他...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.79,1:22:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博迪還是達菲  之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.00,1:22:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你還記得達菲最後怎樣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.67,1:22:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在學校發現他  穿了裙子 戴著有花的帽子以後？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.01,1:22:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被迫站在學校外面...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.68,1:22:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著裙子 戴著花帽子  作為懲罰
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.55,1:22:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒想過  我們為什麼叫他達菲？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.22,1:22:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他奇怪的行為吧 我猜
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.06,1:22:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是「水仙花」的略稱
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.53,1:22:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得這個娘炮最後怎樣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.61,1:22:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 他...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.20,1:22:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六周之後 他開槍自盡
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.24,1:22:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.20,1:22:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都感謝上帝  我的兒子們不用遭受如此折磨
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.21,1:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.42,1:22:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願要個死人  也不願要個娘炮的兒子
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.39,1:23:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我來教你怎麼跳舞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.77,1:23:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.97,1:23:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 把它拿到這裡來  - 是
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.27,1:23:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 你是什麼時候接到這單的？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.48,1:23:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有陣子了  我想應該是1931年11月
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.82,1:23:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綁架案的3個月前
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.32,1:24:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.91,1:24:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伐木場是現金交易的  沒有留下任何收據或者名字
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.53,1:24:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少告訴我們  在犯案之前他都在哪裡買東西
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.58,1:24:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我指一指  那些贖金鈔票都出現在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.62,1:24:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,456號西三街
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.63,1:24:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有476號西三街
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.30,1:24:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有下面這條街這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.30,1:24:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道要找的人是誰了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.80,1:24:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在這一片生活工作了很長時間的人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.14,1:24:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還在那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.60,1:24:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他身高普通  有藍眼睛
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.90,1:24:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高顴骨 尖下巴
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.98,1:24:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 尖下巴  還有口音 像是...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.32,1:24:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德國口音 大概？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.15,1:24:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個有高顴骨的德國人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.66,1:24:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...會給他惹麻煩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.45,1:24:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒幹壞事就不會  我們是聯邦調查局的 我們是好人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.50,1:24:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是沃爾特·萊爾存的錢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.00,1:24:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在列剋星敦大道和127街路口  開了個加油站
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.34,1:25:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是沃爾特·萊爾？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.42,1:25:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得用這個付錢的男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.30,1:25:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得  他買了89分錢的汽油
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.93,1:25:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用這個付錢的？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.85,1:25:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但我不認識他  那之後就沒有見過
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.27,1:25:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他再來  你能認出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.19,1:25:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能啊 他是德國人吧 我想  我是說 有那種口音 還有尖下巴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.69,1:25:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 還有高顴骨 是嗎？  - 是啊 我覺得這鈔票挺好笑的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.53,1:25:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我拍胸脯說  他家裡還有這一樣的一百多張
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.20,1:25:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他聊了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.49,1:25:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 就這些了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.58,1:25:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 萊爾先生
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.79,1:25:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有記下車牌號
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.37,1:25:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是寫在鈔票邊上的那個號碼
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.13,1:25:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.89,1:25:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 叫上托爾森
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.06,1:25:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西斯科探員
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.40,1:26:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紐約機動車辦公室  說這是一輛1930年的藍色道奇轎車
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.28,1:26:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車主是一個德國出生的木匠
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.40,1:26:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在布朗克斯的東222街1279號
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.91,1:26:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字叫布魯諾·理查德·哈普特曼
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.13,1:26:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行動
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.38,1:26:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1934年9月19日...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.76,1:26:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們抓到這個  美國頭號通緝犯之前
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.76,1:26:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被當地警察要求停車  因為車尾燈壞了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.18,1:26:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.85,1:26:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停車
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.61,1:26:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦調查局！  舉起手來！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.03,1:26:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 舉起手來！  - 有問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.07,1:26:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下車！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.50,1:27:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布魯諾·哈普特曼
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.71,1:27:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你因涉嫌綁架及謀殺小查爾斯·林德伯格  而被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.80,1:27:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他銬起來
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.31,1:27:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於抓到了他
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.48,1:27:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要將他定罪  但不像以前的那些審判
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.81,1:27:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有法醫 專家證人  還有證據
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.32,1:27:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要起個標題  加裡森調查員
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.95,1:27:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.37,1:27:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正忙呢 甘迪
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.33,1:27:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,磁帶送來了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.50,1:27:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到我的私密辦公室去
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.84,1:27:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些就可以了  加裡森調查員
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.27,1:28:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想說...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.15,1:28:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐在那個酒吧對面的時候太美了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.74,1:28:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你在盯著我
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.70,1:28:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得承認...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.74,1:28:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你好長時間了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.62,1:28:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢一點
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.12,1:28:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.42,1:28:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來把這脫了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.67,1:28:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轉過去
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.72,1:28:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.20,1:28:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 我跟你說了不能打擾
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.74,1:28:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.54,1:29:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是緊急事件  珊科林探員從達拉斯來電
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.33,1:29:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.08,1:29:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓甘迪小姐讓我通話
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.79,1:29:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 探員？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.55,1:29:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統被槍殺了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.63,1:29:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰知道這件事？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.18,1:29:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有人  我想你應該在媒體之前知道
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.77,1:29:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝  - 不用
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.53,1:29:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 感覺真棒
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.05,1:30:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上把我接到羅伯特·肯尼迪
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.19,1:30:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.11,1:30:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯尼迪先生  總統剛剛被槍殺了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.20,1:30:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.78,1:30:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生？什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.49,1:30:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.84,1:30:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在領先的是「冷山」...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.05,1:30:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領先一個半身位
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.30,1:30:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「爵士」在第三位 落後六個身位
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.85,1:30:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「巴掌傑克」第四位  「大明星梅瑞爾」落後四分之三個身位
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.56,1:30:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始衝刺 「冷山」在左邊  領先一個半身位
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.52,1:30:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五號 要追上了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.03,1:30:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還是「冷山」領先
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.15,1:30:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定我是不是押了他
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.53,1:31:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我們又輸了 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.91,1:31:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「德克斯托」落後半個身位
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.50,1:31:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「德克斯托」開始啟動了  芬德利抽打了他
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.75,1:31:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.67,1:31:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油 德克斯托 加油！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.51,1:31:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他的鞋子了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.13,1:32:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德斯·阿納茲？（音樂家 演員）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.38,1:32:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那雙上面有很醜帶扣的  鱷魚皮鞋？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.05,1:32:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.77,1:32:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得他們有那麼多錢  就不該對時尚敏感點嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.60,1:32:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者至少雇個對時尚敏感的人
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.02,1:32:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 還有他那個人造一樣的老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.77,1:32:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走進來的時候 我都覺得會有獵人  一槍把她的帽子給轟了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.74,1:32:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣 你看 就像...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.74,1:32:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 是啊 那些羽毛
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.54,1:32:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 我真的很在乎你  克萊德 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.83,1:32:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.39,1:32:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.89,1:32:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.80,1:32:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.48,1:32:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想問你一件事 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.98,1:32:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.32,1:33:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得那個女演員  桃樂絲·拉莫爾怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.65,1:33:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和魯迪·瓦力在斯托克俱樂部的那個？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.45,1:33:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 就是她
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.49,1:33:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說是太女性化了吧 但是...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.71,1:33:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在想 要她跟我一起
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.17,1:33:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚餐？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.80,1:33:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 不是晚餐
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.67,1:33:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經一起吃過晚餐好幾次了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.01,1:33:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.93,1:33:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 在紐約  我週末去那裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.52,1:33:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.06,1:33:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想...我想要說的是...  克萊德...是...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.40,1:33:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是時候有個胡佛夫人了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.66,1:33:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜歡她嗎？  是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.71,1:33:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別讓我這麼難堪 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.00,1:34:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有  我沒有想讓你難堪
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.30,1:34:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們...你們有做過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.81,1:34:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.06,1:34:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 克萊德？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.48,1:34:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我一直過不了完整的生活？  這是你想要的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.52,1:34:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你來說 只算是半吊子？
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.28,1:34:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 給我馬上把這杯子撿起來！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.24,1:34:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不我不會！我沒理由這樣做！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.99,1:34:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕！來啊 炒了我
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.91,1:34:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快啊 現在就炒了我！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.37,1:34:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜一下  這行為太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.08,1:34:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.08,1:34:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德！你沒穿鞋子 天哪！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.75,1:34:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不會  我不要聽你說了！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.59,1:34:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠不能對我發號施令了！  你沒有這個權利！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.59,1:34:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 住口！  - 我看透你了！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.51,1:34:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是個膽小的 沒良心的  差勁的小人！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.93,1:34:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.51,1:35:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以後膽敢再這樣做
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.14,1:35:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.64,1:35:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.98,1:35:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 你去哪？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.11,1:35:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 求你了  不要留下我！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.74,1:35:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.07,1:35:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 對不起！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.99,1:35:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 不要離開我！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.99,1:35:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 求求你了！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.33,1:35:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了 克萊德！  克萊德 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.00,1:36:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.75,1:36:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 我們還有一天的賽馬要看
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.10,1:36:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以後要是再提起任何女性朋友...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.77,1:36:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再也不會出現在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.95,1:36:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.66,1:36:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.21,1:36:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米特爾看上去挺有希望
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.56,1:37:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 克萊德？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.06,1:37:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.77,1:37:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去叫醫生
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.32,1:37:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.65,1:37:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去叫醫生！  快去叫醫生！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.74,1:37:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德 看著我 看著我
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.83,1:37:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點去叫醫生啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.58,1:37:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急救！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.25,1:37:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的身體機能大部分都能恢復...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.25,1:37:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但經歷如此一次中風  會限制他的工作時間
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.42,1:37:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及他可以處理的信息量
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.17,1:37:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 胡佛先生？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.59,1:37:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 我只是...  我週六在院子裡和狗玩了一會兒
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.26,1:37:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能只是脫水了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.10,1:37:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是原因  但您也減少一些工作時間可能更明智
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.39,1:37:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在您這個年紀  休息很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.48,1:37:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 讓我們單獨談談
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.78,1:37:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼跟你說吧  你要是膽敢再在我的同事面前說我的不是...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.36,1:37:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會讓你前途盡毀  明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.45,1:38:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.45,1:38:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.29,1:38:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西可以補充能量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.29,1:38:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有節食的藥物  可以有所幫助
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.79,1:38:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果我減掉點體重  就會有更多能量？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.46,1:38:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要擔心您的體重  那是結實的重量
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.51,1:38:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.47,1:38:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安排一下日常的檢查
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.51,1:38:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.48,1:38:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要把諾貝爾和平獎頒給馬丁·路德·金了  你相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.32,1:38:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些敗類和激進分子  已經在國際上都被捧起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.49,1:38:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像1920年的情況又回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.99,1:38:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.00,1:38:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當他發現  我們有這卷錄音帶...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.79,1:38:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道他真正是怎樣一個人...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.17,1:38:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定要拒絕領獎  克萊德 相信我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.96,1:38:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約翰遜總統...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.21,1:38:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.84,1:38:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 克萊德  - 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.18,1:39:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得學著簡潔一點說話  我好像都要聽不懂你了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.26,1:39:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的問題是  我們沒有合法的手段
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.43,1:39:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我們的法律還沒跟上...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.19,1:39:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天這些犯罪分子不斷進步的戰術
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.02,1:39:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.07,1:39:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.53,1:39:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有在媒體的朋友 對吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.36,1:39:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們捏造故事 讓他們...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.45,1:39:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些可疑的激進分子的行為  全部暴露出來
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.00,1:39:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會追蹤消息來源
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.50,1:39:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非都是真的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.00,1:39:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這就叫反間諜 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.17,1:39:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故事越是被捏造  影響力就越戲劇化
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.67,1:39:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我要把這個賓館錄音帶...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.84,1:39:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和一封私人信件一起  在諾貝爾獎頒獎前一天寄給他
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.39,1:39:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他接受了這個獎  我們就直接把錄音帶發到媒體
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.02,1:39:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定你想要捲入  這次的監視？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:55.07,1:39:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什麼這封信  不會是我寫的
Dialogue: 0,1:39:57.78,1:40:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會是捏造成  他自己手下寫的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.74,1:40:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不允許任何的翻錯了  我不確定我們能...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.50,1:40:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不懂你在說什麼了 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.25,1:40:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要學著說話有點底氣
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.22,1:40:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我要你明天來辦公室  這次沒得商量
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.22,1:40:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.73,1:40:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當然行
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.81,1:40:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.60,1:40:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會看到這麼長時間以後  她終於能把我的雞蛋做好了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.11,1:40:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這注射的都是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.45,1:40:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是維他命...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.86,1:40:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一些提神的
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.34,1:40:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「看看你的內心」
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.92,1:41:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你知道你自己是個大騙子  對我們所有黑人都有責任」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.93,1:41:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是「我們」  甘迪 「我們」 不是 「我」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.80,1:41:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您現在是黑人了？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.43,1:41:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我說的每個字都寫下來  明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.48,1:41:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「這個國家的白人騙子已經夠多了...」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.15,1:41:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「但他們這次沒有...」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.32,1:41:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「沒有任何人能和你相比」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.40,1:41:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 「我要重申...」  - 這是做什麼用的？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.49,1:41:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 我在口述的時候沒時間回答問題  快寫
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.79,1:41:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我要重申 你是一個大騙子  充滿罪惡 狠毒的人」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.92,1:41:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你並不信仰上帝  你並不信仰任何道德準則！」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.92,1:41:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能問問這封信要寄給誰...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.38,1:41:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題不是寄給誰  甘迪 不是寄給誰
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.09,1:41:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是誰寄的 並且絕對不是從這裡寄出的  明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.51,1:41:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你其實不是一個領導人...」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.93,1:41:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「而是一個放蕩的 變態的  道德低下的人」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.60,1:41:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「只有一件事你能做了  你也知道怎麼做」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.52,1:41:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「只有這條出路  你最好接受...」
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.19,1:42:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「在你這些骯髒的 變態的 欺詐的行為  暴露在這個國家之前」
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.44,1:42:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都記下來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.91,1:42:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 埃德加  - 打出來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.24,1:42:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打出來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.21,1:42:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解到你在我們人事部門工作  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.04,1:42:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的現在兩年了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.92,1:42:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你應該熟悉我早期的工作...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.26,1:42:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對抗愛德華·克拉克  還有他的3K黨 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.89,1:42:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.22,1:42:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他因為違反販賣白奴法  的暴力行為而被捕...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.39,1:42:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他穿越州界  跟一個白人女人有婚外情
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.94,1:42:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.15,1:42:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那是那時候我處理過的最高的法律了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.40,1:42:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道  我非常為那件事自豪
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.57,1:42:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪小姐告訴我  您上次停在了布魯諾·哈普特曼的逮捕這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.12,1:42:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 您想要從那裡開始嗎？  - 是的 就從那裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.42,1:42:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈普特曼被送去庭審
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.38,1:43:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間是1935年1月1日
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.92,1:43:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H. L. 門肯（記者）稱  這是基督復活以來最大的新聞
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.43,1:43:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在的情況看  可能還要更大
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.22,1:43:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看  沒有兩把鋸子會形成一樣的斷面
Dialogue: 0,1:43:12.81,1:43:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布魯諾·哈普特曼工具箱中的鋸子  留下的鋸痕...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.60,1:43:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和犯罪現場留下的梯子的痕跡一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.56,1:43:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比較贖金字條和哈普特曼的筆跡...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.15,1:43:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把「anything（任何事）」寫成「anyding」  把「good（好）」寫成「gut」
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.03,1:43:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把「boat（船）」寫成「boad」  並且注意這些寫反了的大寫的「N」
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.70,1:43:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這些看上去像「J」的「Y」
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.87,1:43:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格先生  你說你聽到了聲音...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.12,1:43:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那天晚上的典禮上
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.63,1:43:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.04,1:43:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個說話聲  我非常肯定...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.80,1:43:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是用一個外國口音叫康登醫生
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.63,1:43:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「嘿 醫生」
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.80,1:43:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.01,1:43:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽過一樣的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.97,1:43:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.64,1:43:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上的典禮你聽到的聲音是誰的...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.81,1:43:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說道「嘿 醫生」？
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.81,1:44:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是哈普特曼的聲音
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.15,1:44:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他到底是不是單獨行動的？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.28,1:44:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他從未承認  但這些反社會的人什麼時候承認過？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.37,1:44:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證據確鑿
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.28,1:44:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被控訴犯有一級謀殺  同時犯下重大盜竊
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.71,1:44:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在新澤西  這是死罪
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.17,1:44:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈普特曼先生
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.54,1:44:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天 在這個法庭 你有機會...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.17,1:44:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出所有真相
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.38,1:44:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有說過真相嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.97,1:44:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經說過了
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.34,1:44:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那些...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.60,1:44:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對弗萊律師的陳述  你對他說的都是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:36.97,1:44:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某種程度來說
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.43,1:44:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那從某種程度來說 你沒說出真相  是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.19,1:44:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這塊板子是從你的衣櫥找到的  寫了「S-204」
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.11,1:44:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫了這些數字
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.03,1:44:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有點模糊了是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.03,1:44:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.49,1:44:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這之間還有幾個字  看上去像「迪凱特」和「賽德維克」
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.45,1:45:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見沒有？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.29,1:45:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這是什麼意思吧？  那裡的地址？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.04,1:45:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不大清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.59,1:45:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不是康登醫生的住址和電話...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.72,1:45:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,付了贖金的人..
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.38,1:45:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的字跡  在你的衣櫥裡找到
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.47,1:45:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生 醫生來看你了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.85,1:45:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在馬丁·路德·金的歷史性演講以後...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.15,1:45:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人說那一天重新喚醒了  這個國家的良知
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.15,1:45:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而其他人則稱這是國家的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.74,1:45:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在人與人互相殘殺的歷史長河裡  這是充滿希望的一天
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.57,1:45:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個夢想...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.99,1:45:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有一天...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.62,1:45:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家會站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.50,1:45:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發掘信條的真正含義
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.09,1:45:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人留下的東西由故事的結尾決定  歐文斯探員
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.80,1:45:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚好好想想  明天做決定
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.47,1:45:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是關乎個人的遺產？
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.43,1:46:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是整個機構的名譽？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.43,1:46:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩者是相關的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:03.44,1:46:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前者引出了後者 反之亦然
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.10,1:46:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日安
Dialogue: 0,1:46:09.40,1:46:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.11,1:46:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們陪審團 判定被告  布魯諾·理查德·哈普特曼...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.65,1:46:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯有一級謀殺罪
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.79,1:46:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官大人  我請求立即宣判
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.80,1:46:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據州法律
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.59,1:46:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我判決布魯諾·哈普特曼死刑
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.06,1:46:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此時此地  一切依據法律
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.82,1:46:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈普特曼被判死刑了！
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.16,1:47:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世紀大審判...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.66,1:47:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪分子伏法  聯邦調查局成為了公眾的英雄
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.63,1:47:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的結尾 探員
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.51,1:47:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他是不是單獨犯案的？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.55,1:47:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時是不是他本人帶走了孩子？  你怎麼能確定？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.72,1:47:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鐵證如山  我們發現了...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.81,1:47:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,揭開了真相 確認了一切  你不能有什麼爭議了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.85,1:47:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是克拉倫斯·達洛懷疑過  - 當然
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.19,1:47:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 歐文斯探員  他懷疑過
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.36,1:47:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯福夫人發佈了一項聲明  質疑了他的罪行
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.07,1:47:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到非美國人的行為呢  她自己有的是東西要遮掩
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.74,1:47:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您覺得這個作為結尾合適  我會努力做好
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.12,1:47:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 好的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.83,1:47:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.92,1:47:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起看這個
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.22,1:48:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他昨晚收到了我的信和錄音帶
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.22,1:48:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約翰遜總統..
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.39,1:48:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用了100多支筆簽名
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.64,1:48:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一份令人垂涎的紀念品  會頒發給諾貝爾獎得主...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:07.77,1:48:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...馬丁·路德·金  一位盡心盡責的領導人...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.19,1:48:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說吧 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.36,1:48:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 這很有風險  在這些負面報道之後
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.53,1:48:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他故意讓周圍圍繞著一群共產主義分子...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.24,1:48:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了這些他正在集合的力量  他現在正是我們國家內部最大的威脅
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.20,1:48:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代表諾貝爾獎委員會...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.75,1:48:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們把這個...  - 他會拒絕這個獎的 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.75,1:48:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道我們手裡的東西可以毀了他
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.42,1:48:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這項諾貝爾獎  證書 和金牌
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.31,1:48:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.89,1:48:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他完了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.07,1:48:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接受這項諾貝爾和平獎...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.28,1:49:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此刻美國有2200萬黑人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.62,1:49:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正在...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.97,1:49:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾了  您的下一個約見的人到了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.14,1:49:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甘迪 讓醫生先進來
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.65,1:49:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 當然
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.32,1:49:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他幾分鐘後進來 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.94,1:51:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要堅強 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.31,1:52:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要堅強 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:52:18.60,1:52:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要堅強
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.42,1:52:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遊行隊伍正在向前...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.46,1:52:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去往國會大廈的就職儀式
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.51,1:52:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到羅斯福軍樂隊  正在帶路
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.27,1:53:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汽車隊伍正在沿著賓夕法尼亞大道前進
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.06,1:53:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,載著我們的第37任總統
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.20,1:53:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德·米爾豪斯·尼克松向群眾招手
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.04,1:53:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 總統和他的夫人...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.58,1:53:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高興地揮手
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.08,1:54:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當道德敗壞...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.20,1:54:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好人不做任何事...
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.54,1:54:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡就會興盛
Dialogue: 0,1:54:09.92,1:54:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每個公民都有義務瞭解這些
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.09,1:54:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威脅到他們的家園和孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:54:21.60,1:54:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個沒興趣也不願意  從過去吸取教訓的社會
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.73,1:54:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注定會隕滅
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.99,1:54:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠不能忘記歷史
Dialogue: 0,1:54:39.74,1:54:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠不能放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.17,1:54:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至今天 仍舊有組織  把美國作為他們的頭號目標
Dialogue: 0,1:54:55.43,1:54:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會毀掉每個人的平安和幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.89,1:55:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把我們推入無法無天的深淵
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.47,1:55:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超乎想像的無恥
Dialogue: 0,1:55:08.98,1:55:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生可以見您了  胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.98,1:55:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.62,1:55:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 進來
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.47,1:55:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我很抱歉 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.51,1:55:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直不接電話
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.77,1:55:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和一位要退休的探員有會議
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.60,1:55:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就要走了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.02,1:55:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.86,1:55:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他今天不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:56:00.03,1:56:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能幫我們安排一下晚餐？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.04,1:56:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們轉角的餐廳 老地方
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.37,1:56:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕他今天真的太累了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.04,1:56:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你願意去他家裡吃？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:12.38,1:56:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:56:16.13,1:56:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,1:56:18.22,1:56:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 謝謝你 甘迪
Dialogue: 0,1:56:26.77,1:56:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海倫？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.06,1:56:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.07,1:56:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是毀了一切我所愛的？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.07,1:56:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還沒有離開 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.58,1:56:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們親手建立的一切？
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.58,1:56:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:56:53.17,1:56:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查局比開始只有我們的時候  要強大多了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.21,1:57:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的部下很可靠  他們保證著國家的安全
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.47,1:57:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海倫 假如...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.35,1:57:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我出了什麼事  我需要你做點事 你明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.48,1:57:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.61,1:57:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼克松 他會追查一切
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.20,1:57:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會毀了我和我的調查局
Dialogue: 0,1:57:28.49,1:57:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心假如我不在  會發生些什麼事
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.63,1:57:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的機密文件？
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.09,1:57:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會找到這些文件
Dialogue: 0,1:57:45.30,1:57:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 海倫
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.65,1:58:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他們給你施加多少壓力？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.36,1:58:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管多少？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.36,1:58:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.99,1:58:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管施加多少壓力
Dialogue: 0,1:58:10.50,1:58:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,1:58:14.17,1:58:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 海倫
Dialogue: 0,1:58:27.76,1:58:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼克松有沒有讓你辭職？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.27,1:58:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他想要知道  我們掌握了他的什麼文件
Dialogue: 0,1:58:36.35,1:58:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.52,1:58:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說「什麼文件？」
Dialogue: 0,1:58:41.53,1:58:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他知道
Dialogue: 0,1:58:43.86,1:58:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想讓我們擴大我們的竊聽範圍  包括新聞報道員 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:58:49.95,1:58:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能那樣做  尤其是現在
Dialogue: 0,1:58:53.45,1:58:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題就在這 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:58:55.33,1:59:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不答應他做這些暗地裡的事  他會成立自己的私人集權
Dialogue: 0,1:59:00.67,1:59:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 那是違法的
Dialogue: 0,1:59:03.55,1:59:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他雖然沒有直說  但我可以從他眼神裡看出來
Dialogue: 0,1:59:09.39,1:59:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不會受任何人控制 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.56,1:59:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個威脅  他會為了權力做任何事
Dialogue: 0,1:59:16.73,1:59:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:19.56,1:59:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你看 我從不跟他玩這些  這就是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.07,1:59:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如我做的某些事情  看上去有些過界...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.70,1:59:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他們需要找出  他們都做了些什麼...
Dialogue: 0,1:59:30.28,1:59:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來讓他們感到被勒索或是恐嚇
Dialogue: 0,1:59:34.25,1:59:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想的不是這個
Dialogue: 0,1:59:37.50,1:59:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？你在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:42.59,1:59:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 或許是時候我們該退休了
Dialogue: 0,1:59:47.43,1:59:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,1:59:50.72,1:59:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有很偉大的成就 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,1:59:54.35,1:59:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在就收手  你會得到嘉獎
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.52,2:00:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你一直想要的 不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:00.77,2:00:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個國家長久的崇拜？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.61,2:00:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在就是你獲得這些的機會
Dialogue: 0,2:00:06.94,2:00:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊 我憑什麼不呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:10.53,2:00:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我憑什麼不呢 克萊德？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:12.33,2:00:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保衛國家不受布爾什維克侵略
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.04,2:00:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掃除了激進分子  逮捕了「機關鎗凱利」
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.12,2:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了迪林傑 抓住了卡佩斯  還把布魯諾·哈普特曼定罪了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:23.75,2:00:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我還有最後一口氣  想要保衛這個國家...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:27.51,2:00:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻被強制要求退休？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.18,2:00:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會被打倒的  你這建議其實讓我...
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.14,2:00:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑你的忠心
Dialogue: 0,2:00:36.56,2:00:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的忠心 埃德加？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:38.77,2:00:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你的忠心 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,2:00:42.27,2:00:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讀過你的手稿了 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,2:00:46.15,2:00:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你並沒有逮捕卡佩斯
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.65,2:00:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一樣清楚  那條街上沒有白馬
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.82,2:00:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後座也沒有槍
Dialogue: 0,2:00:56.99,2:01:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是你殺了迪林傑的  是博維斯探員
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.00,2:01:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你把所有的榮譽據為己有
Dialogue: 0,2:01:06.21,2:01:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「機關鎗凱利」也從未說過  「不要開槍 官老爺們」
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.51,2:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你編造了這些  來賣出漫畫書 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.52,2:01:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於本世紀最大的犯罪案件
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.90,2:01:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,林德伯格先生根本沒有出來  和你握手
Dialogue: 0,2:01:27.11,2:01:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有表達他對調查局的信任
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.74,2:01:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說你是挑剔的傢伙  拒絕再次和你見面
Dialogue: 0,2:01:40.37,2:01:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是你逮捕了哈普特曼
Dialogue: 0,2:01:44.17,2:01:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是西斯科探員
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.63,2:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至都不在現場 埃德加  只有那張照片
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.30,2:01:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 你寫的大多數都是誇大其詞
Dialogue: 0,2:01:55.51,2:02:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多是明顯的謊言  我甚至都不知道你是否意識到這一點
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.77,2:02:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.06,2:02:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以對所有人說話  對全世界
Dialogue: 0,2:02:09.23,2:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看在你自己份上  看在調查局的份上
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.61,2:02:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你騙不了我
Dialogue: 0,2:02:19.24,2:02:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不應該給你這份工作 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.42,2:02:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.92,2:02:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不符合要求
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.30,2:02:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你記得那天你進來面試嗎？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.47,2:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.27,2:02:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來到我的辦公室  幫我整理好了窗戶
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.81,2:02:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拿了我的手帕
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.94,2:02:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把它遞給我的
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.99,2:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你記不記得為什麼我會出汗？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.20,2:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你剛剛鍛煉過
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.95,2:03:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:04.50,2:03:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出汗是因為我...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:07.29,2:03:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一刻我知道...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.30,2:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一刻我清楚地知道...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:15.13,2:03:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,2:03:18.30,2:03:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這輩子從未需要過其他任何人
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.06,2:03:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從未像你這樣
Dialogue: 0,2:03:27.52,2:03:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我開始出汗
Dialogue: 0,2:03:30.86,2:03:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.99,2:03:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,埃德加 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.49,2:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 這是...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:40.95,2:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是消化不良 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.75,2:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天出去吃晚飯吧？  我們的老地方
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.59,2:03:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧如果我感覺好些了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:56.34,2:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,2:03:58.26,2:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.68,2:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須...  我們還有很重要的事情要商量
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.64,2:04:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在在調查局  我沒有任何人可以信任
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.02,2:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能靠你了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.50,2:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.43,2:04:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 克萊德
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.52,2:04:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 埃德加
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.05,2:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家 胡佛先生
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.76,2:05:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 安妮
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.97,2:05:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波佐 波佐 好孩子 過來
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.80,2:05:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民主的本質...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.18,2:05:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扎根於對於獨立的信仰
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.27,2:05:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命的意義已經超越任何人造系統
Dialogue: 0,2:05:38.78,2:05:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛是世上最偉大的力量
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.11,2:05:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比仇恨要持久得多
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.83,2:05:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是人類那些非自然的種群
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.47,2:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:04.34,2:06:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是胡佛先生家的安妮
Dialogue: 0,2:06:07.97,2:06:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛先生去世了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:44.17,2:06:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.18,2:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個老不死的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.60,2:06:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要準備一個演講  要上電視
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.43,2:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.10,2:06:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先封鎖他的辦公室 換掉鎖  做你應該做的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.56,2:07:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得把那些該死的文件找出來
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.03,2:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.04,2:07:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.54,2:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:21.92,2:07:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在樓上
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.51,2:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們  這於我個人也是極大的損失...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.01,2:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已得知  J·埃德加·胡佛先生去世了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.68,2:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位了不起的公僕  為國家工作了48年
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.02,2:09:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為聯邦調查局的局長  歷經8任總統
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.85,2:09:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用他無與倫比的奉獻精神  能力 以及巨大貢獻
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.86,2:09:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25年以來 從我第一次以新人國會議員  的身份來到華盛頓
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.07,2:09:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我最親密的朋友和顧問之一
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.54,2:10:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為 每個美國人  都欠了胡佛先生很多
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.62,2:10:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把聯邦調查局  建立成了最好的法律執行機構
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.21,2:10:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在全世界的範圍來說
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.96,2:10:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已下令所有的政府機構  都要下半旗致哀
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.05,2:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要說 這樣做  為了埃德加·胡佛
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.89,2:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有了他頑強的勇氣  和極其險惡的攻擊作鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,2:10:24.77,2:10:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經保證  聯邦調查局的旗幟會一直高高飄揚
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.24,2:10:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦調查局是美國永恆的豐碑
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.24,2:10:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「即使這最親密的臉龐..」
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.25,2:10:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「會隨著時間的流逝而消失...」
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.29,2:10:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「我清楚地記得  你的眼睛裡有挑逗的笑容」
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.67,2:10:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「還有那最溫柔的地方...」
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.59,2:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「是東北方位之於你溫柔的嘴角」
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.50,2:11:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡佛的「私人機密檔案」從未被人知曉  只有一些沒有歸檔的資料透露出線索
Dialogue: 0,2:11:07.50,2:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德·托爾森繼承了胡佛的房產 搬進了他家  接受了覆於他棺木的美國國旗
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.50,2:11:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊德·托爾森的葬在離胡佛  在國會墓地的墓碑幾碼遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:11:17.50,2:11:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,=完=  翻譯：米粒@豆瓣
